{"story_json":"{\"storyPhases\":[{\"phaseID\":\"P1\",\"SegmentList\":[{\"SegmentID\":\"S1\",\"preSegID\":[],\"nextSegID\":[\"S2\"],\"fillImageURL\":\"\",\"Location\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationDesc\":\"我需要一张基于这个场景，然后背景是太阳花从的中景照片，背景稍微虚化一点\",\"LocationImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"],\"LocationVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"],\"desc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对称式三分法构图，视觉引导线由一条蜿蜒的石板路向画面深处延伸。[前景描述] 画面左下角和右下角是盛开的鲜艳花丛与带露水的绿叶，边缘略微模糊以增强景深感。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央偏下是一座精致的木制栅栏门，旁边放置着一个空藤篮，右侧三分之二处有一丛高大的向日葵。[背景深度] 远处是一座欧式风格的乡村小屋，屋檐下挂着风铃，背景延伸至柔和起伏的绿色山丘。[光影效果] 柔和的清晨金黄色阳光从左上角斜射入画面，在石板路上投下斑驳的树影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774114871586\",\"label\":\"我需要一张基于这个场景\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"],\"desc\":\"我需要一张基于这个场景，然后背景是太阳花从的中景照片，背景稍微虚化一点\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774114871586\"},\"Characters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774104228496\",\"CharacterImageDict\":{\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\":135,\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\":224}},{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterDesc\":{\"age_gender\":\"30-year-old woman\",\"hair\":\"neatly tied up brown hair\",\"eyes\":\"gentle brown eyes\",\"skin\":\"fair skin\",\"body_type\":\"average build\",\"base_outfit\":\"long rustic apron dress\",\"signature_items\":[]},\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"30-year-old woman\",\"hair\":\"neatly tied up brown hair\",\"eyes\":\"gentle brown eyes\",\"skin\":\"fair skin\",\"body_type\":\"average build\",\"base_outfit\":\"long rustic apron dress\",\"signature_items\":[]},\"children\":[]}]}],\"EventList\":[{\"EventID\":\"S1-E1\",\"preEventID\":\"\",\"nextEventID\":\"S1-E2\",\"EventDesc\":\"In the early morning,  Little Red Riding Hood 's  garden  was bathed in soft golden light. Her  mother  handed her a basket of pastries and said, \\\" Grandmother  is ill. Take these to her, and do not stray from the  path .\\\"\",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterDesc\":{\"age_gender\":\"30-year-old woman\",\"hair\":\"neatly tied up brown hair\",\"eyes\":\"gentle brown eyes\",\"skin\":\"fair skin\",\"body_type\":\"average build\",\"base_outfit\":\"long rustic apron dress\",\"signature_items\":[]},\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"30-year-old woman\",\"hair\":\"neatly tied up brown hair\",\"eyes\":\"gentle brown eyes\",\"skin\":\"fair skin\",\"body_type\":\"average build\",\"base_outfit\":\"long rustic apron dress\",\"signature_items\":[]},\"children\":[]}]}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对称式三分法构图，视觉引导线由一条蜿蜒的石板路向画面深处延伸。[前景描述] 画面左下角和右下角是盛开的鲜艳花丛与带露水的绿叶，边缘略微模糊以增强景深感。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央偏下是一座精致的木制栅栏门，旁边放置着一个空藤篮，右侧三分之二处有一丛高大的向日葵。[背景深度] 远处是一座欧式风格的乡村小屋，屋檐下挂着风铃，背景延伸至柔和起伏的绿色山丘。[光影效果] 柔和的清晨金黄色阳光从左上角斜射入画面，在石板路上投下斑驳的树影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Narrator\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Type\":\"Environment\",\"Actant\":{},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"A European rustic cottage with wind chimes hanging under the eaves, set against softly rolling green hills. The entire landscape is bathed in bright, soft golden morning sunlight streaming from the top left, casting clear shadows.\"},\"Focalization\":\"Zero\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc91bce814b4804698b5d952468cbd6ee8\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Narrator\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Type\":\"Environment\",\"Actant\":{},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"A symmetrical composition focusing on a winding stone path extending into the distance. In the slightly blurred foreground, vibrant blooming flowers and green leaves are covered in morning dew. A delicate wooden fence gate stands in the center, with tall sunflowers growing on the right.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc08a3244d3e46459c84999e9d94ec3aa3\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Mother stands gracefully on the winding stone path, bathed in the soft sunlight. She is wearing a long rustic apron dress, and her neatly tied up brown hair catches the morning light.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"On the stone path near the wooden fence gate, with the tall sunflowers visible in the background.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc7ba804b0d75545febf87ada142952ffb\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Little Red Riding Hood stands facing her mother, her small frame clad in a white pinafore dress with blue trim. Her signature red hooded cloak is draped over her shoulders.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Standing on the stone path opposite Mother, framed by the dew-covered flowers in the foreground.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc45caffc709524c958533f9a6586581b9\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Mother gently extends her arms forward, offering a woven wicker basket filled with fresh pastries toward Little Red Riding Hood.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"Internal\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scb62e5327d95447dc8a5c49270a630cbf\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S6\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Reaction\":\"Little Red Riding Hood reaches out with both hands and firmly grips the handle of the wicker basket.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"Zero\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc232bef2565e543fdac6e08e35880d523\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S7\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\"],\"Type\":\"Dialogue\",\"Actant\":{\"Dialogue\":\"Grandmother is ill. Take these to her, and do not stray from the path.\",\"Action\":\"Mother looks down with gentle brown eyes, her expression earnest and slightly concerned as she speaks.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"Zero\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc247d50750f144de592eecf99ee523f74\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S8\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Reaction\":\"Little Red Riding Hood nods solemnly, her large round brown eyes looking up attentively at her mother. Her small fingers tighten slightly around the handle of the basket.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc06fa58dbd71946dd9739809264293c10\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The scene reveals a quiet European country cottage, sitting peacefully among rolling emerald green hills. Bright and soft golden morning light pours down from the top left of the frame, casting a warm halo over the entire landscape and projecting clear, elongated shadows on the rolling meadow.\",\"ShotSize\":\"LS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright and soft golden morning light shines from the top left, creating clear shadows and a high-contrast warm halo.\",\"Hue\":\"Vibrant emerald green as the main tone, blended with the warm golden yellow brought by the sunlight.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features a large expanse of emerald green meadow. In the midground, a rustic European country cottage stands quietly, occupying the lower center of the frame. The background consists of rolling emerald hills and a clear blue sky. Bright golden morning light pours down from the top left, casting clear shadows on the grass and the cottage. The overall tone is warm and bright, filled with a peaceful morning atmosphere.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B1_46a5ba.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Wind chimes gently sway under the eaves of the rustic cottage, while the morning breeze softly rustles the emerald green grass. The golden sunlight casts slowly shifting shadows across the peaceful meadow.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B1_7ee1a55e580648cc8b87008de2422994.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B1_7ee1a55e580648cc8b87008de2422994.mp4\"]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt7910ac174a6b4596ac5277a51eeb2086\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera slowly pushes in, shifting the visual focus from the open landscape to the details of the cottage's eaves. A delicate set of wind chimes hangs beneath the mottled wooden eaves, swaying gently in the breeze, reflecting the golden morning sunlight and exuding a peaceful sense of life.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Side-backlighting, the morning sunlight hits the surface of the wind chimes to form sharp highlights, while the area under the eaves is in soft shadow, creating rich contrast between light and dark.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm wooden brown intertwines with the metallic luster of the wind chimes, while the background reveals a softly blurred greenery.\",\"Prompt\":\"Blurred edges of wooden eaves serve as a foreground occlusion. In the midground, a delicate set of metallic wind chimes hangs under the eaves, occupying the left-center of the frame. The background is softly blurred green hills and blue sky. Morning light hits the wind chimes from the top left, sparkling with dazzling golden light. The overall tone is warm and peaceful, full of a sense of life.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B2_467672.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The delicate metallic wind chimes hang beneath the mottled wooden eaves, swaying gently in the morning breeze and reflecting the golden sunlight.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling of leaves in the breeze accompanied by the gentle, melodic tinkling of metallic wind chimes.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B2_3111d27531d44130a993f6646ab09df9.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B2_3111d27531d44130a993f6646ab09df9.mp4\"]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt211e502757cd48acb9ba7cef53de4f9b\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The line of sight moves down, and the frame presents a perfectly symmetrical composition. A winding stone path stretches into the distance. In the foreground, delicate flowers and green leaves covered in morning dew are slightly blurred in front of the lens. Right in the center of the frame is an exquisite wooden fence gate, and on the right side grow tall sunflowers, blooming brightly towards the morning sun.\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Morning sunlight from the top left pours down, highlighting the dew on the petals and leaves. The wooden fence gate casts a clear diagonal shadow on the stone path.\",\"Hue\":\"Dominated by vibrant bright green and the bright yellow of sunflowers, dotted with the gorgeous colors of various wildflowers, creating a cheerful and bright mood.\",\"Prompt\":\"Vibrant flowers and green leaves covered in morning dew form a slightly blurred natural frame in the foreground. In the exact center of the midground is an exquisite wooden fence gate. On the right stand several tall sunflowers. A winding stone path passes through the wooden gate and extends into the background, disappearing into the distant mist. Sunlight shines down from the top left, illuminating the dew on the petals. The overall tone is vibrant, presenting a perfect symmetrical beauty.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B3_821163.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Morning dew gently sparkles on the vibrant blooming flowers and green leaves in the foreground. The tall sunflowers on the right sway softly in the gentle morning breeze.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The soft rustling of leaves in the gentle morning breeze, accompanied by the faint, peaceful chirping of birds in the distance.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btc589858aebb446eebe687f2c9bdf95eb\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Mother stands elegantly on the winding stone path, her posture upright. The morning light pours down like a light veil, plating a warm golden outline on her neatly tied brown hair. She wears a rustic long country apron dress. Behind her, the wooden fence and tall sunflowers sway gently in the breeze, creating a peaceful and serene morning atmosphere.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft morning side light shines from the left, forming a warm rim light on the character's hair and skirt hem. The background features mottled light and shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm natural tones, dominated by the bright yellow of sunflowers, the warm brown of the soil, and the plain colors of the dress.\",\"Prompt\":\"Blurred edges of a wooden fence form a slight foreground occlusion in the lower left corner. In the midground, Mother stands elegantly on the winding stone path, facing off-screen left, occupying about two-thirds of the height in the center-right of the frame. She wears a long country apron dress, her brown hair neatly tied up. The background features tall sunflowers swaying in the morning light. Soft morning glow shines from the left side of the frame. The overall tone leans towards a warm orange-yellow.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\",\"x\":67.4,\"y\":12.7,\"width\":26.4,\"height\":83.8,\"Rotation\":\"Facing off-screen left\",\"Posture\":\"Standing elegantly\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B4_b8eb8e.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Mother stands quietly and elegantly, gazing gently off-screen left. In the background, tall sunflowers sway gently in the morning breeze.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling of sunflower leaves swaying in the gentle morning breeze.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt7f0d453846cb45f5837b6a2ec34eb99d\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B6\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Reverse shot, Little Red Riding Hood stands obediently on the stone path opposite her mother. Her small body is wrapped in a white apron dress with blue edges, and the iconic red hooded cloak on her shoulders is particularly striking in the sunlight. In the foreground, several flowers covered in crystal dew nod gently in the breeze, making her look like an elf from a fairy tale.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright natural lighting, backlighting outlines highlights on the edge of the red cloak, and the dew in the foreground refracts fine, sparkling light spots.\",\"Hue\":\"Fresh and bright tones, with the emerald green of the garden as the main tone. Little Red Riding Hood's bright red cloak forms a strong visual center.\",\"Prompt\":\"Vibrant wildflowers covered in crystal dew intertwine at the bottom of the frame to form a beautiful blurred foreground. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood stands on the stone path, looking up slightly, facing off-screen right, occupying about half the height in the center-left of the frame. She wears a white apron dress with blue edges and a bright red hooded cloak over her shoulders. The background features a winding path extending into the distance and soft morning mist. Bright backlighting outlines her petite silhouette. The overall tone is fresh with a sharp contrast between red and green.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":40,\"y\":55,\"width\":30,\"height\":55,\"Rotation\":\"Facing off-screen right\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, looking up slightly\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B5_c95a56.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood stands obediently, looking up slightly and quietly watching her mother off-screen right. The dew-covered flowers in the foreground nod gently in the breeze.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling of leaves and a gentle morning breeze.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt133b490f8cd242d698c9b9670e60d448\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B6\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B5\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B7\",\"BeatDesc\":\"From Little Red Riding Hood's subjective over-the-shoulder perspective, Mother wears a gentle smile, her arms gently reaching forward, handing a wicker basket full of freshly baked pastries towards the camera.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Over-the-Shoulder\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright natural morning light pours from the top right, outlining soft rim light on Mother's face and the pastries. The background greenery forms mottled light spots.\",\"Hue\":\"Dominated by warm orange-yellow and natural emerald green, highlighting a warm and caring atmosphere.\",\"Prompt\":\"The blurred edge of Little Red Riding Hood's red hood serves as foreground occlusion in the lower left corner. In the midground, Mother wears a gentle smile, occupying about half the height in the center, facing the camera slightly to the left. She holds a wicker basket full of golden pastries with both hands, extending it towards the camera. The background features blurred lush greenery and blooming flowers in the garden. Bright morning light pours from the top right. The overall tone is warm and soft.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":40,\"width\":45,\"height\":60,\"Rotation\":\"Front-Left\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, extending arms holding a basket\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":15,\"y\":70,\"width\":30,\"height\":40,\"Rotation\":\"Back-Right\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, seen from behind\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B6_f95875.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Mother gently extends her arms forward, offering a woven wicker basket filled with fresh pastries toward the camera, maintaining a warm and gentle smile.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle morning breeze rustling through the garden leaves, accompanied by faint birdsong.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B6_3afe54f51dfe4055b45c9e0e6f36e75b.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B6_3afe54f51dfe4055b45c9e0e6f36e75b.mp4\"]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btb0caaa2db768407b92068468b102354c\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B7\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B6\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B8\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera pulls back to a side objective perspective, showing their interaction in the garden. Mother stands on the right, maintaining the posture of handing the basket. Little Red Riding Hood is on the left, reaching her hands forward, ready to receive the wicker basket from her mother.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft natural side light illuminates their profiles and sides. The light forms a visual focus on the basket between them, with shadows naturally cast on the ground.\",\"Hue\":\"Fresh natural green intertwines with warm wood colors. Little Red Riding Hood's bright red cloak forms a strong color accent in the frame.\",\"Prompt\":\"The foreground features several clear, dew-covered low shrubs. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood stands on the left and Mother on the right facing each other, occupying most of the frame's width. Mother is handing the wicker basket to the left, and Little Red Riding Hood reaches out with both hands ready to receive it. The background shows the wooden fence surrounding them and the European-style wooden cottage in the distance. Soft side light illuminates both figures. The overall tone is fresh and natural.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":30,\"y\":50,\"width\":35,\"height\":75,\"Rotation\":\"Right-Profile\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, reaching out with both hands\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\",\"x\":70,\"y\":45,\"width\":35,\"height\":80,\"Rotation\":\"Left-Profile\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, holding out a basket\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B7_9bc4c7.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood reaches out with both hands from the left side of the frame and firmly grips the handle of the wicker basket held out by Mother on the right.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling of leaves in the garden breeze and faint, peaceful birdsong.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B7_2eb08cc7db6f44fea851678306bf7d86.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B7_2eb08cc7db6f44fea851678306bf7d86.mp4\"]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt01be6385d0e24c54bc31490839213c0b\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B8\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B7\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B9\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera cuts to a close-up. Little Red Riding Hood's petite hands enter the frame from the left, her fingers tightly gripping the rough wicker basket handle, meeting Mother's hands at the edge of the basket. The texture of the pastries is clearly visible.\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Strong localized natural light shines directly on the meeting hands and the basket handle, highlighting the rough wicker texture and skin details. The background is in soft shadow.\",\"Hue\":\"Dominated by the warm brownish-yellow wicker and skin tones. The background is a highly blurred and darkened deep green, forming a strong color contrast to highlight the subject.\",\"Prompt\":\"The foreground features the blurred edges of Mother's fingers. The midground close-up focuses on the finely woven handle of the wicker basket, occupying the core area of the frame. Little Red Riding Hood's petite hands tightly grip the handle from the left. The background is completely blurred into soft green and earth-toned light spots. Sunlight shines directly on the basket and hands, highlighting the texture of the skin and wicker.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":40,\"y\":50,\"width\":40,\"height\":40,\"Rotation\":\"Right-Profile\",\"Posture\":\"Hands firmly gripping the basket handle\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\",\"x\":80,\"y\":50,\"width\":30,\"height\":30,\"Rotation\":\"Left-Profile\",\"Posture\":\"Hands gently supporting the basket\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B8_d91a37.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's petite hands enter the frame from the left, her fingers tightening to firmly grip the rough wicker basket handle, meeting Mother's hands at the edge of the basket.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling sound of wicker as hands firmly grip the basket handle.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B8_a9f2840c10fa48ed86a680a461ded8b3.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S1-E1-B8_a9f2840c10fa48ed86a680a461ded8b3.mp4\"]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btc246ed4b65bd4905b82f044151bdb09c\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B9\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S7\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B8\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B10\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera looks over Little Red Riding Hood's shoulder, focusing on Mother's gentle face. Mother lowers her head slightly, her eyes revealing sincere care and a hint of worry, softly giving instructions to her daughter about going to Grandmother's house. The garden breeze brushes by gently, and the sunlight leaves soft light and shadow on her face.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft natural side light, sunlight shining through the gaps in the leaves, highlighting Mother's facial contours and gentle eyes.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm earth tones and the natural green of the garden as the main tones, dotted with a touch of red in the foreground.\",\"Prompt\":\"The blurred edge of Little Red Riding Hood's red hood and shoulder form a natural foreground occlusion in the lower left corner. In the midground, Mother occupies about half the space on the right side of the frame, looking down slightly, her eyes gentle and worried. The background features mottled tree shadows and a wooden fence in the garden softly blurred in the depth of field. Warm yellow sunlight pours in from the left side of the frame, illuminating Mother's face. The overall tone leans towards warm orange.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\",\"x\":70.7,\"y\":18.6,\"width\":40,\"height\":70,\"Rotation\":\"Facing left-down\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, looking down gently\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\",\"x\":15.3,\"y\":57.5,\"width\":28.7,\"height\":90.5,\"Rotation\":\"Back to camera\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, facing away\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B9_f30364.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Mother looks down earnestly with gentle eyes, her expression softening with a hint of worry as she speaks to Little Red Riding Hood. The garden breeze gently brushes by, subtly moving the leaves and her hair.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft garden breeze rustling the leaves.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S1-E1-S7-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Line\":\"Grandmother is \\\\ill. Take these\\\\ to her, and do\\\\ not stray from\\\\ the path.\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Gentle, caring, and slightly worried adult female voice\"}],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"videoUrl\":\"\"},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt6507ef5c5f20458bae157de09b71e20e\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B10\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S8\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B9\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B11\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera cuts, looking down at Little Red Riding Hood over Mother's arm. As the camera slowly pushes in, Little Red Riding Hood looks up, her round brown eyes intently watching her mother. Her expression looks particularly solemn, and she nods earnestly.\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Over-the-Shoulder\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Top-side light illuminates Little Red Riding Hood's face, clear catchlights sparkling in her pupils. The background features soft circular light spots.\",\"Hue\":\"The bright red hood contrasts sharply with the greenery of the surroundings. The overall tone is warm and has an oil painting texture.\",\"Prompt\":\"Mother's blurred arm foreground occlusion on the right side of the frame. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood (not wear hat)is on the left side of the frame, lifting her tender face. Her large brown eyes look up intently, her expression serious. The background consists of green grass and low flower bushes on the garden ground, softly blurred. Sunlight shines down from the top, forming highlights on the red hood. The overall tone is warm with an oil painting texture.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":20,\"y\":20,\"width\":45,\"height\":60,\"Rotation\":\"Facing right-up\",\"Posture\":\"Looking up, nodding solemnly\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Mother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Mother_ae1872.png\",\"x\":84,\"y\":4.7,\"width\":30,\"height\":100,\"Rotation\":\"Back to camera\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, facing away\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B10_cf36dc.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood nods solemnly, her large round brown eyes looking up attentively at her mother. Her small fingers tighten slightly around the handle of the basket.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft ambient sounds of a gentle garden breeze and faint rustling of leaves.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btf4091bbef36a422bab3f7ca11f9a0455\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E1-B11\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E1-S8\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E1-B10\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The line of sight moves down, and the camera pulls in extremely close. Little Red Riding Hood's tender little hands are tightly gripping the rough woven basket handle. Her small fingers tighten due to slight exertion, silently conveying her inner tension and determination.\",\"ShotSize\":\"ECU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft natural diffused light emphasizes the rough texture of the vines and the delicate three-dimensionality of the hands, with no harsh shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm brown wood tones intertwine with the highly blurred red and green in the background, with high color purity.\",\"Prompt\":\"No obvious foreground occlusion in the frame. The midground features an extreme close-up of Little Red Riding Hood's tender little hands right in the center of the frame. Her fingers are tightening slightly, firmly gripping the rough woven basket handle. The background is a completely blurred red skirt hem and garden grass. Delicate natural diffused light highlights the texture of the woven vines and the skin of the hands. Warm brown intertwines with blurred red and green.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":30,\"y\":20,\"width\":40,\"height\":60,\"Rotation\":\"Profile\",\"Posture\":\"Hands gripping the basket handle tightly\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B11_45de27.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's small fingers tighten slightly, gripping the rough woven basket handle firmly.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Faint rustling of the woven basket handle and soft ambient garden sounds.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btcbf1627117904ed4a31f3438fd77e9e6\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":false,\"contains_confrontation\":false,\"contains_revelation\":false,\"emotional_shift\":false}},{\"EventID\":\"S1-E2\",\"preEventID\":\"S1-E1\",\"nextEventID\":\"\",\"EventDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood nodded, fastened her bright red cloak, and set off toward Grandmother's house.\",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对称式三分法构图，视觉引导线由一条蜿蜒的石板路向画面深处延伸。[前景描述] 画面左下角和右下角是盛开的鲜艳花丛与带露水的绿叶，边缘略微模糊以增强景深感。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央偏下是一座精致的木制栅栏门，旁边放置着一个空藤篮，右侧三分之二处有一丛高大的向日葵。[背景深度] 远处是一座欧式风格的乡村小屋，屋檐下挂着风铃，背景延伸至柔和起伏的绿色山丘。[光影效果] 柔和的清晨金黄色阳光从左上角斜射入画面，在石板路上投下斑驳的树影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Little Red Riding Hood stands near the delicate wooden fence gate, wearing a white pinafore dress with blue trim, holding the wicker basket firmly in her hands.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"The sunlit garden path bordered by blooming flowers and green leaves with morning dew.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sce492f3671ca24bf39d46dfae7ce3a77b\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"She raises her small hands to her neck and carefully ties the ribbons of her bright red hooded cloak into a secure, neat bow.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc6c6f6cd812fb492fbe4d09468a365ad7\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Lowering her hands, she turns her body toward the winding stone path, her shoulder-length brown hair swaying slightly as she takes her first confident step forward.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc7817bbd261d24930b7ffc583d3f5a6c2\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"She pushes the wooden gate open, her bright red cloak fluttering slightly in the morning breeze as she steps out of the garden.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc34583a84f7cb400f95a1065b35a6911d\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"旁白\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Type\":\"Pause\",\"Actant\":{},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"The wooden gate gently swings shut. The small figure in the bright red cloak walks further down the sunlit stone path, heading toward the rolling green hills in the distance.\"},\"Focalization\":\"Zero\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scfd34b00df43f4e0c9a85f77ae93d97d4\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E2-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S1-E2-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood stands in the center of the garden near the closed delicate wooden gate, holding her wicker basket.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm golden and vibrant green.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft golden morning sunlight from the top left, casting dappled tree shadows on the stone path.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm golden and vibrant green.\",\"Prompt\":\"Blurred blooming flowers and green leaves with morning dew form a natural foreground frame. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood stands facing slightly towards the camera near a delicate wooden fence gate, occupying the center of the frame, holding a wicker basket. In the background, a winding stone path leads to a rustic cottage under a soft sky. Soft, golden morning sunlight shines from the top left, casting dappled shadows, creating a warm and bright anime style atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B1_f4ab57.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对称式三分法构图，视觉引导线由一条蜿蜒的石板路向画面深处延伸。[前景描述] 画面左下角和右下角是盛开的鲜艳花丛与带露水的绿叶，边缘略微模糊以增强景深感。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央偏下是一座精致的木制栅栏门，旁边放置着一个空藤篮，右侧三分之二处有一丛高大的向日葵。[背景深度] 远处是一座欧式风格的乡村小屋，屋檐下挂着风铃，背景延伸至柔和起伏的绿色山丘。[光影效果] 柔和的清晨金黄色阳光从左上角斜射入画面，在石板路上投下斑驳的树影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\