. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood is seen in full figure, pushing the delicate wooden gate open and stepping through it, her bright red cloak fluttering in the breeze. The background opens up to show the path extending towards distant green hills. Clear morning sunlight illuminates the scene, casting distinct shadows on the ground, creating a fresh and adventurous atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B4_eb7371.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L1\",\"LocationName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对称式三分法构图，视觉引导线由一条蜿蜒的石板路向画面深处延伸。[前景描述] 画面左下角和右下角是盛开的鲜艳花丛与带露水的绿叶，边缘略微模糊以增强景深感。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央偏下是一座精致的木制栅栏门，旁边放置着一个空藤篮，右侧三分之二处有一丛高大的向日葵。[背景深度] 远处是一座欧式风格的乡村小屋，屋檐下挂着风铃，背景延伸至柔和起伏的绿色山丘。[光影效果] 柔和的清晨金黄色阳光从左上角斜射入画面，在石板路上投下斑驳的树影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_75ecbc.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood pushes the wooden gate open with her hand and steps out of the garden, her bright red cloak fluttering slightly in the morning breeze.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The squeak of a wooden gate opening, followed by soft footsteps on a stone path and the gentle rustling of leaves in the breeze.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S1-E2-B4-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt55cd3f240f5148cbbfab9487161870aa\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S1-E2-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S1-E2-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S1-E2-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The wooden gate swings shut in the foreground while the small figure of Little Red Riding Hood walks away down the sunlit path.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\