haracterImageURL\":\"\",\"Line\":\"The wooden gate\\\\ gently swings \\\\shut. The small\\\\ figure in the \\\\bright red cloa\\\\k walks further\\\\ down the sunli\\\\t stone path, h\\\\eading toward t\\\\he rolling gree\\\\n hills in the \\\\distance.\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Calm, peaceful narrative voice\"}]},\"BeatType\":\"Pause\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S1-E2-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt83e83de2473349ff96a58fd490823f2f\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":false,\"contains_confrontation\":false,\"contains_revelation\":false,\"emotional_shift\":false}}],\"position\":{\"x\":-18435.538190855277,\"y\":-5928.024025350258}}]},{\"phaseID\":\"P2\",\"SegmentList\":[{\"SegmentID\":\"S2\",\"preSegID\":[\"S1\"],\"nextSegID\":[\"S3\"],\"fillImageURL\":\"\",\"Location\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"更加广阔的视角，鸟瞰机位\",\"LocationImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Forest_path_7adbc3.png\",\"/RefImage/Forest_path_3bd0c4.png\",\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"],\"LocationVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"],\"desc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774265550861\",\"label\":\"更加广阔的视角\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Forest_path_7adbc3.png\",\"/RefImage/Forest_path_3bd0c4.png\"],\"desc\":\"更加广阔的视角，鸟瞰机位\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774265689151\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"顺着图片中的小路往前走，小路延伸至远方\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"LocationImageDict\":{\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\":58},\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774265550861\"},\"Characters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_5eb2aa.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"male wolf\",\"hair\":\"thick gray fur\",\"eyes\":\"sharp yellow eyes\",\"skin\":\"fur-covered\",\"body_type\":\"large, muscular and lean build\",\"base_outfit\":\"none\",\"signature_items\":[\"sharp teeth\"]},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774102345269\",\"label\":\"趴下变成正常的狼\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"desc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774102345269\",\"CharacterImageDict\":{\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\":129}}],\"EventList\":[{\"EventID\":\"S2-E1\",\"preEventID\":\"\",\"nextEventID\":\"S2-E2\",\"EventDesc\":\"Sunlight filtered through the dense canopy, casting dappled shadows along the winding  forest path .  Little Red Riding Hood  walked along with her basket, humming a cheerful tune. Beside a towering  oak tree , a  wolf  suddenly stepped into her  path . \",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_5eb2aa.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"male wolf\",\"hair\":\"thick gray fur\",\"eyes\":\"sharp yellow eyes\",\"skin\":\"fur-covered\",\"body_type\":\"large, muscular and lean build\",\"base_outfit\":\"none\",\"signature_items\":[\"sharp teeth\"]},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774102345269\",\"label\":\"趴下变成正常的狼\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"desc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774102345269\"}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_7adbc3.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks briskly along the winding dirt road, her bright red hooded cloak glowing vividly under the dappled sunbeams filtering through the dense canopy.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"A sunlit forest path extending diagonally, surrounded by vibrant green foliage, with a few butterflies fluttering near the lower left corner.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"She swings her woven basket lightly with one hand, her lips parted slightly as she hums a cheerful tune, her shoulder-length brown hair bouncing with each step.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"A large, muscular figure covered in thick gray fur stands half-concealed behind the massive trunk of the towering oak tree, his sharp yellow eyes locked intensely onto the approaching girl.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"A large, muscular figure covered in thick gray fur stands half-concealed behind the massive trunk of the towering oak tree, his sharp yellow eyes locked intensely onto the approaching girl.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc44722de7f9c54834bbc265e855c66ae2\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"He steps smoothly out from the shadows of the oak tree, his heavy paws landing silently on the fallen leaves as he moves into the center of the sunlit dirt road, completely blocking the way.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sceac8904d2ab84a23a1ff32f76eba42f0\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Reaction\":\"Her footsteps halt abruptly, her small hands gripping the handle of the basket tightly, knuckles turning pale, as her large round brown eyes widen at the sight of the blocking figure.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"Zero\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks along the winding dirt road from the lower right towards the upper left, her red cloak vibrant against the green forest.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Vibrant, warm, and cheerful\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright Tyndall light beams filter down from above, casting dappled shadows on the path.\",\"Hue\":\"Vibrant, warm, and cheerful\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features blurred oak roots and swaying wildflowers with fluttering butterflies. Midground shows Little Red Riding Hood, a young girl in a red hooded cloak, walking briskly along a diagonal dirt road from lower right to upper left, occupying a small portion of the frame. Background reveals a deep forest with layered dense canopy and faint mist between tree trunks. Bright Tyndall light beams filter down from above, casting dappled shadows on the path, creating a vibrant, warm, and cheerful anime style.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B1_a879ed.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B1_ba08dacae5c4443ca86ede7ff0a23798.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B1_ba08dacae5c4443ca86ede7ff0a23798.mp4\"],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks briskly along the winding dirt road from the lower right towards the upper left, her red cloak swaying. Butterflies flutter in the foreground.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of leaves, distant bird chirps, and light, rhythmic footsteps on the dirt path.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E1-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's upper body and face. She smiles with parted lips, her brown hair bouncing, as her hand swings the woven basket.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Lively, warm, and optimistic\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Worm's-eye View\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright Tyndall light beams filter down from above, casting dappled shadows on the path.\",\"Hue\":\"Vibrant, warm, and cheerful\",\"Prompt\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks forward in the forest, taking a side photo of her footsteps\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B2_06800b.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B2_3c571293bfca41ce8690acb7e9eda193.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B2_3c571293bfca41ce8690acb7e9eda193.mp4\"],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks forward, bouncing her shoulder-length brown hair with each step. She smiles warmly with parted lips and playfully swings her woven basket lightly with one hand.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"A cheerful humming tune from Little Red Riding Hood, accompanied by light footsteps, rustling leaves, and a lively forest ambiance.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E1-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"reuse\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E1-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"A large, muscular wolf covered in thick gray fur stands half-hidden behind a massi