 the approaching girl from the cool shadows.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Low, tense ambient forest sounds with a subtle rustling of leaves and a faint, eerie atmospheric hum.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E1-B3-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt2d91dabcf1864a3ba44b77080f016081\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E1-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The muscular wolf steps out from the shadows of the giant oak tree, positioning himself in the middle of the sunlit dirt road on all fours.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Dramatic and intimidating\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Strong Tyndall light beams strike the wolf from above, highlighting his thick gray fur against the darker forest backdrop.\",\"Hue\":\"Dramatic and intimidating\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features fallen dry leaves scattered on the dirt path. Midground shows the large, muscular wolf on all fours, standing squarely in the center of the sunlit road, completely blocking the path, looking imposing. Background displays the towering oak tree and the winding path fading into the misty forest depth. Strong Tyndall light beams strike the wolf from above, highlighting his thick gray fur against the darker forest backdrop, establishing a dramatic and intimidating mood.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B4_bb19f3.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B4_6ae93554e41f43c1aa655b3c9ce44dce.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B4_6ae93554e41f43c1aa655b3c9ce44dce.mp4\"],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly Out\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The muscular wolf steps smoothly out from the shadows of the giant oak tree, his heavy paws landing silently on the fallen leaves. He walks into the center of the sunlit dirt road on all fours and stops, imposing and completely blocking the path.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Rustling of dry leaves under heavy paws, accompanied by a low, intimidating ambient drone.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E1-B4-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btf67fc0d4a31a479f979a48ce8b0bd858\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E1-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E1-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood from the waist up. Her large round brown eyes widen in shock, and her pale-knuckled hands grip the handle of the woven basket tightly.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Tense and fearful\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"A slight shadow falls across her face to emphasize her alarm, contrasting with the bright blurred background.\",\"Hue\":\"Tense and fearful\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground shows the tightly gripped woven basket with pale knuckles. Midground features Little Red Riding Hood from the waist up, her large round brown eyes wide open in sudden shock, her cheerful expression gone. Background is a heavily blurred forest environment with dark tree trunks. A slight shadow falls across her face to emphasize her alarm, contrasting with the bright background, conveying a sudden tense and fearful mood.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B5_910b31.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B5_7284eb59c5a248298f8fa0df5f4a3eab.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B5_7284eb59c5a248298f8fa0df5f4a3eab.mp4\"],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood comes to an abrupt halt, freezing in place. Her hands grip the handle of her woven basket tightly, knuckles turning pale, as her large round brown eyes widen in sudden shock.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The sound of abrupt, crunching footsteps suddenly stopping, followed by a tense, eerie silence and a subtle heartbeat-like low drone.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E1-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":false,\"contains_confrontation\":false,\"contains_revelation\":false,\"emotional_shift\":false}},{\"EventID\":\"S2-E2\",\"preEventID\":\"S2-E1\",\"nextEventID\":\"S2-E3\",\"EventDesc\":\" Wildflowers swayed in the breeze, and butterflies danced among the blossoms. She slowed her pace, savoring the peaceful scene. \\\"Where are you headed, little girl?\\\" he asked with a friendly smile. \\\"I'm going to visit my sick grandmother and bring her some pastries,\\\" she replied innocently. \",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_5eb2aa.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"male wolf\",\"hair\":\"thick gray fur\",\"eyes\":\"sharp yellow eyes\",\"skin\":\"fur-covered\",\"body_type\":\"large, muscular and lean build\",\"base_outfit\":\"none\",\"signature_items\":[\"sharp teeth\"]},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774102345269\",\"label\":\"趴下变成正常的狼\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"desc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774102345269\"}],\"EventLocat