\"She stops completely, her shoulders relaxed. She looks up at the towering figure with innocent curiosity, her hands gently resting on the handle of her woven basket.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc87bee6352a6f4caf827544e2d4ffbad2\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E2-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Dialogue\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"She smiles back warmly, lightly lifting the basket with both hands to show it to him.\",\"Dialogue\":\"I'm going to visit my sick grandmother and bring her some pastries.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc7bb345076c844336bf002e9627d7cb1c\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E2-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E2-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E2-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood slows her pace on the left side of the frame, her eyes following a butterfly fluttering towards the right.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm golden and vibrant green tones.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright natural sunlight filtering from above, creating clear Tyndall light shafts and dappled shadows on the path.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm golden and vibrant green tones.\",\"Prompt\":\"Blurred swaying wildflowers frame the bottom foreground. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood stands on the left side of the dirt path, wearing her red hooded cloak and holding a basket, her head tilted up to watch a small butterfly. The background features a towering oak tree and a winding forest path bathed in dappled sunlight filtering through the dense canopy. Clear Tyndall effect light shafts shine down from the top. Warm, vibrant anime style.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B1_b1a70c.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '10-year-old girl', 'hair': 'shoulder-length brown hair', 'eyes': 'large round brown eyes', 'skin': 'fair skin', 'body_type': 'slim build, small frame', 'base_outfit': 'white pinafore dress with blue trim', 'signature_items': ['red hooded cloak', 'basket']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood slows her walking pace, her head tilting slightly as her large round brown eyes track a butterfly fluttering towards the right above the swaying wildflowers.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling of leaves in the gentle breeze and faint, distant birdsong.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"videoUrl\":\"\"},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E2-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt228aac933ce8495881d4e2c9def4f2ed\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E2-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E2-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E2-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E2-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The muscular Wolf stands on the right side of the path, bathed in sunlight, lowering his head to form a wide, friendly smile.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm golden sunlight contrasting with the cool, misty greens of the deep forest.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Sunlight hits the Wolf's thick gray fur from above, highlighting his silhouette against the slightly misty forest background.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm golden sunlight contrasting with the cool, misty greens of the deep forest.\",\"Prompt\":\"Out-of-focus oak tree roots and leaves create a natural frame in the right foreground. In the midground, a large, muscular Wolf with thick gray fur stands on the right side of the sunlit path, facing left with a wide, friendly smile. The background shows the deep, misty forest with layered tree canopies and soft light rays piercing through the leaves. Anime style, crisp lines.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B2_54a0b6.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': 'male wolf', 'hair': 'thick gray fur', 'eyes': 'sharp yellow eyes', 'skin': 'fur-covered', 'body_type': 'large, muscular and lean build', 'base_outfit': 'none', 'signature_items': ['sharp teeth']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":55,\"y\":25,\"width\":18.1,\"height\":57.7,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E2-B2_231b805dcaf4467c9215ba7eadf1d3b6.mp4\",\"VideoUrl\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E2-B2_231b805dcaf4467c9215ba7eadf1d3b6.mp4\"],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The muscular Wolf stands still in the sunlit path, slightly lowering his large head and curving his mouth into a wide, friendly smile.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of leaves and subtle forest ambiance.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E2-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btea4f90863c4e44c9a5fdd8a9fe265836\"},{\"Bea