te\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt9c1b4f967f794e92a001dcb9e525df91\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E3-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E3-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E3-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E3-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood turns her head from the left to the right, squinting her eyes with a curious expression.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm, inviting, dominated by the bright red of the cloak and lush greens.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft, warm sunlight illuminating her face, creating gentle highlights on her red cloak.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm, inviting, dominated by the bright red of the cloak and lush greens.\",\"Prompt\":\"A blurred edge of a woven basket sits in the lower left foreground. In the midground, a 10-year-old girl with a red hooded cloak and white pinafore dress occupies the center, turning her head towards the right side of the frame, her brown eyes squinting with curiosity. The background is a beautifully blurred forest path with warm dappled light. Makoto Shinkai anime style, crisp lines.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E3-B4_769e05.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood turns her head from left to right, following the 