Url\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Vibrant clusters of wildflowers sway gently in the breeze along the winding side path, while a few butterflies flutter gracefully in the foreground. Dust motes dance softly within the bright Tyndall light beams filtering through the dense oak tree canopy.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of leaves in the breeze, distant chirping of forest birds, and a soft, magical ambient hum.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reveal\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E2\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E3-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btb467d9fefb8d4ffa9fa5690d5a4fbab6\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E3-B6\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E3-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E3-B5\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E3-B7\",\"BeatDesc\":\"A close-up view focusing on the vibrant wildflowers swaying gently along the edge of the side path, bathed in golden sunlight.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Bright, colorful, and enchanting.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reveal\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Golden rim light on the flower petals, sparkling bokeh effect in the background.\",\"Hue\":\"Bright, colorful, and enchanting.\",\"Prompt\":\"A few blades of grass blur in the extreme foreground. In the midground, a vibrant cluster of blue and yellow wildflowers occupies the center, their petals crisp and detailed, swaying gently. The background is completely out of focus, showing bokeh circles of golden sunlight and deep forest greens. Makoto Shinkai anime style, cinematic depth of field.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E3-B6_7e080b.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationIm