\"Hue\":\"\",\"Prompt\":\"\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E4-B1_5cbe71.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\",\"x\":49.9,\"y\":20.6,\"width\":21.8,\"height\":69.3,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood stands stiffly, gripping her woven basket tightly. Her eyes dart back and forth between the two paths.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of oak leaves in the wind and subtle ambient forest sounds.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E4-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"reuse\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt65d774bfe7fd4a9f9bd697b8a1b22bc2\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E4-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E4-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's face fills the frame as she tilts her head, catches her lower lip between her teeth, and then breaks into a bright, resolving smile. Her hands, visible at the bottom of the frame, relax their grip on the basket.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm, cheerful, dominated by soft skin tones and vivid red.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft, diffused natural light on the face with a gentle rim light on the hood.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm, cheerful, dominated by soft skin tones and vivid red.\",\"Prompt\":\"Out-of-focus floating dust motes and a hint of a soft leaf edge create a subtle foreground depth. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood's face and shoulders dominate the center of the frame, showing a bright, resolving smile as her hands relax on her basket handle. The background is completely blurred out into soft bokeh of green foliage and brown tree trunks. Soft, diffused natural light illuminates her face, highlighting her large brown eyes and the vivid red of her hood, conveying a warm, cheerful, and relieved tone.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E4-B2_566214.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood tilts her head slightly, catches her lower lip between her teeth in a brief moment of hesitation, and then breaks into a bright, resolving smile as her hands relax their grip on the basket.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle forest ambiance with soft rustling leaves and a subtle, uplifting musical chime.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E4-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt1b44480ffb6946ba90eb71ea48bf126a\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E4-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E4-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood pivots her body away from the camera's original axis, her red cloak flaring out slightly as she turns fully to face the right side of the frame, pointing towards the winding side trail.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Energetic, vibrant reds and earthy browns.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Bright directional sunlight highlighting the motion of the red cloak, creating dynamic shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Energetic, vibrant reds and earthy browns.\",\"Prompt\":\"A few out-of-focus wildflowers sway gently in the lower right foreground. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood occupies the center, captured in mid-pivot with her red cloak flaring out dynamically, her body now facing towards the right side of the frame. The background features the thick, textured trunk of the giant oak tree and the beginning of a leaf-covered dirt path. Bright sunlight catches the motion of her cloak, creating dynamic shadows and a lively, energetic atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E4-B3_26a3f9.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood pivots her body sharply to the right, causing her vibrant red cloak to flare out dynamically. She stops to fully face the winding side trail while the wildflowers in the foreground sway gently in the breeze.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of oak leaves in the breeze, accompanied by the crisp sound of footsteps pivoting on the leaf-covered dirt path and the soft swoosh of a cloak.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E4-B3-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btf9fac25975f4456b8e577d03830e6cf4\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E4-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E4-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood takes eager steps onto the leaf-covered dirt path, walking briskly from left to right past thick, protruding oak roots.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Earthy, warm, adventurous tones of brown, green, and red.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Dappled sunlight on the ground, casting distinct shadows of the tree roots.\",\"Hue\":\"Earthy, warm, adventurous tones of brown, green, and red.\",\"Prompt\":\"Massive, textured oak roots and scattered fallen leaves dominate the lower foreground, creating a low-angle perspective. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood, seen from a full-body perspective, walks briskly from left to right along a dirt path, her basket swinging slightly. The background extends into the forest with a winding trail flanked by bushes and distant trees. Sunlight filters through the canopy, casting a warm, dappled glow on the path, evoking a sense of adventure and forward momentum.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E4-B4_e00eca.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\",\"x\":73,\"y\":23.7,\"width\":14,\"height\":44.5,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks briskly from left to right along the leaf-covered dirt path, stepping past thick oak roots while her basket swings slightly.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The crisp crunch of dry leaves underfoot, accompanied by a gentle forest breeze and distant birdsong.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E4-B4-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btbc54dc4d1ea84b82932ac2f7db1adedb\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E4-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E4-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E4-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"A wide view of the forest path. The small figure of Little Red Riding Hood in her red cloak walks further away down the diagonal trail. Clear Tyndall light beams shine down, and butterflies flutter around wildflowers in the immediate foreground.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Magical, serene, deep forest greens contrasted with the bright red cloak and warm sunlight.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Pause\",\"ShotSize\":\"LS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Dramatic Tyndall light beams shining down from the canopy, illuminating the misty air and the path.\",\"Hue\":\"Magical, serene, deep forest greens contrasted with the bright red cloak and warm sunlight.\",\"Prompt\":\"Vibrant wildflowers and fluttering butterflies fill the immediate foreground, slightly blurred to emphasize depth. In the midground, the small figure of Little Red Riding Hood in her striking red cloak walks away down a diagonal, leaf-strewn dirt path, occupying the center-right of the frame. The background reveals a majestic, deep forest with towering trees, dense canopy, and a subtle mist hanging in the air. Clear, dramatic Tyndall light beams pierce through the leaves from above, illuminating the path and creating a magical, serene, Makoto Shinkai-style anime atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E4-B5_5d07df.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"\",\"LocationName\":\"\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\",\"x\":58.7,\"y\":27.4,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly Out\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood walks further away down the diagonal trail, moving deeper into the forest. In the immediate foreground, butterflies flutter around swaying wildflowers.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of leaves in the forest breeze, subtle fluttering sounds of butterfly wings, and serene magical ambient nature sounds.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S2-E4-S5-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"\",\"CharacterName\":\"Narrator\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Line\":\"The small figur\\\\e in the red cl\\\\oak moves furth\\\\er down the dia\\\\gonal trail, ba\\\\thed in clear T\\\\indall light be\\\\ams, while butt\\\\erflies dance a\\\\round the swayi\\\\ng wildflowers \\\\in the foregrou\\\\nd.\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Calm, serene, storytelling voice\"}]},\"BeatType\":\"Pause\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E4-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt555256468c7449efae1a04daf233594f\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":false,\"contains_confrontation\":false,\"contains_revelation\":false,\"emotional_shift\":false}},{\"EventID\":\"S2-E5\",\"preEventID\":\"S2-E4\",\"nextEventID\":\"\",\"EventDesc\":\"The wolf watched her leave, then dashed off in the other direction.\",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_5eb2aa.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"male wolf\",\"hair\":\"thick gray fur\",\"eyes\":\"sharp yellow eyes\",\"skin\":\"fur-covered\",\"body_type\":\"large, muscular and lean build\",\"base_outfit\":\"none\",\"signature_items\":[\"sharp teeth\"]},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774102345269\",\"label\":\"趴下变成正常的狼\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"desc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774102345269\"}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_7adbc3.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"A large, muscular wolf with thick gray fur steps out from the shadowy side of the massive oak tree, his sharp yellow eyes fixed intently on the distant red cloak.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"The shadowed base of the giant oak tree in the center of the frame, contrasting with the bright Tindall light beams illuminating the path ahead.\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scb1923a1ffcf0485b8c98797ee5d1ac8a\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Reaction\":\"His ears twitch slightly as he watches the girl walk away. His jaw parts just enough to reveal a row of sharp teeth, his body remaining rigidly still and calculating.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scda9843aa5b2248eb9868e825b21c54d8\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"He abruptly pivots his lean, muscular body away from the side trail, lowering his center of gravity as his paws shift silently on the leaf-covered ground.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc2e80ef1710cd4bcfbedb2f17f30bed10\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"The wolf lunges forward with immense power, his hind legs kicking up a burst of dry leaves as he dashes swiftly away down the main winding dirt road.\"},\"Space\":{},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc94a0ec09190d453b899ce7d5f22b553e\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"旁白\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Type\":\"Pause\",\"Actant\":{},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"The winding dirt road is left empty. A few disturbed dry leaves swirl in the air near the thick oak roots, slowly drifting back down into the clear Tindall light beams.\"},\"Focalization\":\"Zero\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E5-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"A large, muscular gray wolf steps out from the deep shadows of the giant oak tree's roots, his sharp yellow eyes gazing intently toward the right side of the frame.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Translucent green and warm yellow, carrying a lurking sense of mystery.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Strong light and dark contrast, with Tindall light beams filtering from above to illuminate local areas, leaving deep shadows behind the subject.\",\"Hue\":\"Translucent green and warm yellow, carrying a lurking sense of mystery.\",\"Prompt\":\"Blurred dewy weeds and thick oak roots form a dark foreground in the lower right corner. In the midground, a massive, muscular gray wolf steps out from the oak's shadow, occupying the left third of the frame. His head is slightly lowered, and his sharp yellow eyes stare intently toward the right side of the frame. The background features overlapping dense tree canopies and faint mist in the deep forest. Sunlight filters through the canopy to form clear Tindall light beams, creating strong contrast. The overall tone is Makoto Shinkai style, with clear translucent greens intertwined with warm yellow.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B1_d5a25f.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The large, muscular gray wolf takes a slow, deliberate step forward from the deep shadows of the oak tree's roots into the edge of the light, pausing to stare intently toward the right side of the frame.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Gentle rustling of leaves in the wind, accompanied by the quiet, heavy footsteps of the wolf stepping onto the forest floor.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E5-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btcda87f82000b428d95213e43b6876cc3\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E5-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Close-up of the wolf's face. His ears twitch slightly, and his jaw parts to reveal a row of sharp, menacing teeth.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Cool green and dark gold, revealing a cold sense of danger and calculation.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Sharp side-top light outlines the facial contours, with highlights concentrated on the sharp teeth and yellow eyes.\",\"Hue\":\"Cool green and dark gold, revealing a cold sense of danger and calculation.\",\"Prompt\":\"A few blurred falling yellow leaves sweep past the lens to form a dynamic foreground. The midground is a close-up of the gray wolf's head, occupying most of the center frame. The wolf's ears are tilted slightly back, and his jaw is slightly open to reveal sharp teeth. His eyes are cold and focused. The background is completely blurred forest scenery with dappled light spots. A sharp top light hits the side of the wolf's face and fangs, highlighting the texture and gloss of his thick gray fur. The overall tone leans towards cool green and dark gold.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B2_772a5c.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The wolf's ears twitch slightly. His jaw slowly parts to reveal a row of sharp, menacing teeth while his head and body remain rigidly still and calculating.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Subtle rustling of falling leaves in the wind, accompanied by an eerie, quiet tension in the forest.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E5-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btd75b74c1d0d4442a8da239be79b29368\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E5-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The wolf pivots his body away from his previous sightline, lowering his center of gravity into a crouch.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Bright natural green and earthy tones of dry leaves, full of physical tension.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Dappled forest light, with the subject in half-light and half-shadow natural lighting.\",\"Hue\":\"Bright natural green and earthy tones of dry leaves, full of physical tension.\",\"Prompt\":\"The edge of the oak tree trunk in the lower right corner serves as a dark foreground obstruction. In the midground, the gray wolf lowers his center of gravity into a crouching posture ready to pounce, occupying the center of the frame. His front paws step on the leaf-covered ground, and his body faces the depth of the dirt road. The background is the winding forest path and sunlit mist. Dappled tree shadows are cast on the wolf's gray fur, and natural light spills from directly above. The overall tone is Makoto Shinkai's bright natural green and earth tones.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B3_d4be9c.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The wolf swiftly turns his muscular body, his paws shifting silently on the dry leaves as he crouches down, lowering his center of gravity into a pouncing posture.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Rustling of dry leaves, subtle forest ambience, and the soft shifting of paws on the ground.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E5-B3-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt7ed4c5e3034149d68f54f7401cd7c4f5\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E5-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The wolf lunges forward powerfully, kicking up a burst of dry leaves, and dashes swiftly down the winding dirt road away from the camera.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm sunlight tones, full of motion and vitality.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"LS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Clear Tindall light beams illuminate the main path, with backlighting outlining the running subject.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm sunlight tones, full of motion and vitality.\",\"Prompt\":\"Flying dry leaves and raised dust form a highly dynamic foreground in front of the lens. In the midground, the back of the gray wolf is seen sprinting violently forward along the winding dirt road, his figure rapidly shrinking in the frame. The background is the deep forest path, towering trees, and glowing mist. Strong Tindall light beams pour down from directly above, illuminating the wolf's running path and the flying fallen leaves. The overall tone is warm and dynamic.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B4_e9cc16.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The wolf explodes into a powerful sprint, its hind legs kicking up a burst of dry leaves as it rapidly dashes away down the winding dirt road, its figure shrinking into the distance.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"A sudden burst of rustling dry leaves followed by the rapid, heavy thudding of paws fading down the dirt path.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E5-B4-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt732d2db158ec4ca0baee98c9a4118ccc\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S2-E5-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S2-E5-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S2-E5-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"An empty winding dirt road illuminated by Tindall light beams. Disturbed dry leaves swirl in the air near the oak roots and slowly drift back to the ground.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Peaceful warm yellow and vibrant green, returning to calmness.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Pause\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft and bright Tindall effect, light full of airy texture, dappled light and shadow on the empty path.\",\"Hue\":\"Peaceful warm yellow and vibrant green, returning to calmness.\",\"Prompt\":\"Thick oak roots and a few clusters of swaying wildflowers form a tranquil foreground in the lower right corner. The midground is an empty winding dirt road, where a few disturbed dry leaves are swirling in mid-air and slowly drifting down. The background features overlapping dense tree canopies and the depths of the forest, with mist faintly visible between the trunks. Sunlight filters through the dense canopy from directly above, forming clear Tindall light beams spilling on the empty path. The overall style is Makoto Shinkai anime, with clear lines and bright, warm natural light.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B5_3171da.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L2\",\"LocationName\":\"Forest path\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"No characters present. Disturbed dry leaves swirl in mid-air near the thick oak roots and slowly drift back down to the ground through the clear Tindall light beams.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft rustling of dry leaves and a gentle, peaceful forest breeze.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S2-E5-S5-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"\",\"CharacterName\":\"Narrator\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"\",\"Line\":\"The winding dir\\\\t road is left \\\\empty. A few di\\\\sturbed dry lea\\\\ves swirl in th\\\\e air near the \\\\thick oak roots\\\\, slowly drifti\\\\ng back down in\\\\to the clear Ti\\\\ndall light bea\\\\ms.\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Calm, peaceful, storytelling voice\"}]},\"BeatType\":\"Pause\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S2-E5-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":false,\"contains_confrontation\":false,\"contains_revelation\":false,\"emotional_shift\":false}}],\"position\":{\"x\":-8931.979884948698,\"y\":-6726.568219164841}}]},{\"phaseID\":\"P3\",\"SegmentList\":[{\"SegmentID\":\"S3\",\"preSegID\":[\"S2\"],\"nextSegID\":[],\"fillImageURL\":\"\",\"Location\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"],\"LocationVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"],\"desc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"children\":[]}],\"LocationImageDict\":{\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\":60}},\"Characters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Ridi