d steps cautiously toward the bed in the shadowy room.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm golden tones mixed with deep, cool blues and purples in the shadows.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Golden sunset light hitting from the right side, contrasting heavily with the dark, cool shadows in the background.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm golden tones mixed with deep, cool blues and purples in the shadows.\",\"Prompt\":\"A blurred edge of a heavy wooden bedframe and a thick blanket form the right foreground, creating a natural framing. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood, occupying the left half of the frame, is pulling back slightly and wiping a tear from her fair cheek, her large round brown eyes looking intently toward the right. The background features the deep, dim corners of the wooden cottage, with scattered objects on the floor. A long, golden ray of sunset light streams in from the right, illuminating her face and the edge of the bed, contrasting with the cool, dark shadows of the room. Cartoon Makoto Shinkai style, clear lines.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E4-B1_23ba9d.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\"