\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":34,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":66,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood tilts her head and points timidly toward the figure in bed as she speaks.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Her small voice trembles in the stillness of the room.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S3-E4-S2-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\",\"Line\":\"Grandmother, why are your eyes so big?\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Young, timid but clear girl voice\"}]},\"BeatType\":\"Dialogue\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E4-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt04cb59be072e402e98e1848aa576ef54\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E4-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E4-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The figure in bed leans into the dim light beneath the wrinkled nightcap, its eyes gleaming strangely from the shadows.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Dark, ominous blues and grays pierced by glowing yellow and orange.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"A sharp, dramatic sliver of golden light slicing across the eyes and snout, surrounded by heavy, dark shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Dark, ominous blues and grays pierced by glowing yellow and orange.\",\"Prompt\":\"In the midground, occupying the right side, the Wolf wearing a wrinkled oversized nightcap leans forward from a pile of thick blankets. Its sharp yellow eyes gleam, and thick gray fur bristles on its face. The background consists of the dark, shadow-filled corner of the cottage bed. A sharp sliver of golden sunset light cuts across the Wolf's eyes and snout, leaving the rest of the body in ominous darkness. Cartoon Makoto Shinkai style.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E4-B3_711c68.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":34,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":66,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The disguised Wolf shifts forward beneath the blankets, revealing its strange eyes.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The room stays hushed except for a faint rustle of bedding.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E4-B3-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btbd8317f61ac74d6aa4cdc26d0de2aa3b\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E4-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E4-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"\\\"The better to see you with, my dear,\\\" the disguised Wolf murmurs from the bed.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Dark, menacing grays and blacks with a harsh, warm highlight.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Dialogue\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Low-key lighting with a rim light highlighting the fur texture and the wetness of the lips and teeth.\",\"Hue\":\"Dark, menacing grays and blacks with a harsh, warm highlight.\",\"Prompt\":\"No distinct foreground. In the midground, taking up almost the entire frame, is the terrifying face of the Wolf, viewed from a slightly low angle. Its long, fur-covered snout is inching forward, and its dark lips are curling up into a sinister, menacing grin, hinting at sharp teeth. The background is completely swallowed by the dark, out-of-focus shadows of the cottage interior. The sunset light catches the texture of the gray fur and the gleam of its wet nose and teeth. Cartoon Makoto Shinkai style, intense and menacing.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E4-B4_665a28.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf leans closer from the bed and answers in a low, eerie voice.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Its answer is soft, but unnervingly calm.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S3-E4-S4-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"Line\":\"The better to see you with, my dear.\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Low, rough, menacing wolf voice\"}]},\"BeatType\":\"Dialogue\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E4-B4-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt2141a0cf96d1445ea6db159b459fb06c\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E4-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E4-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B6\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood edges closer and asks, \\\"Grandmother, why is your mouth so big?\\\" As she speaks, the blankets begin to shift violently.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Vibrant, aggressive warm tones clashing with cool background shadows.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Dialogue\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"High-contrast action lighting, with sunbeams highlighting the flying dust and the Wolf's dynamic pose against the dark room.\",\"Hue\":\"Vibrant, aggressive warm tones clashing with cool background shadows.\",\"Prompt\":\"Thick, heavy blankets flying through the air in a blur create a dynamic foreground. In the midground, the massive, muscular lean body of the gray Wolf is captured mid-lunge, jumping from the right side of the wooden bed toward the left. The background reveals the wide wooden bed and the open wooden wardrobe, lit by the dramatic rays of the setting sun. The lighting emphasizes the explosive motion, with dust motes dancing in the sunbeams. Cartoon Makoto Shinkai style, high action.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E4-B5_09aa49.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCha