 of the saliva. Cartoon Makoto Shinkai style, terrifying impact.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E4-B6_3a310c.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf explodes out from beneath the blankets, jaws opening as it lunges.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The growl erupts into the room with a violent burst of motion.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S3-E4-S5-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"Line\":\"The better to eat you up!\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Low, rough, menacing wolf voice\"}]},\"BeatType\":\"Reveal\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E2\",\"ShotIndex\":2,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E4-B5-S2\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btca6f8c59e249460485c59663f731200d\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E4-B7\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E4-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E4-B6\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood recoils in terror as the massive shadow of the Wolf falls over her.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Fading warm skin tones rapidly overtaken by cold, terrifying dark grays and blacks.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"A fast-moving, harsh shadow completely overwhelming the warm, fading light on the character's face.\",\"Hue\":\"Fading warm skin tones rapidly overtaken by cold, terrifying dark grays and blacks.\",\"Prompt\":\"A massive, dark, ominous shadow of a leaping beast sweeps across the foreground, rapidly covering the subject. In the midground, viewed from a high angle, Little Red Riding Hood's face is frozen in sheer terror, her large round brown eyes widened with pupils shrunk to pinpricks, her mouth slightly open in a gasp. The background is the worn wooden floorboards of the cottage. The remaining sunset light on her face is quickly being swallowed by the harsh, moving shadow of the Wolf. Cartoon Makoto Shinkai style, dramatic and terrifying.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E4-B7_429f37.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood jerks backward as the Wolf surges toward her.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"A sharp gasp cuts through the cottage air.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E4-B6-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt795c9782a98d4c0a92cb75094bcbdd5f\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":false,\"contains_confrontation\":true,\"contains_revelation\":true,\"emotional_shift\":false}},{\"EventID\":\"S3-E5\",\"preEventID\":\"S3-E4\",\"nextEventID\":\"S3-E1\",\"EventDesc\":\"As Little Red Riding Hood drew nearer, the wolf threw off the blankets and lunged at her. She screamed, stumbled backward, and crashed onto the wooden floor, her basket spilling across the room.\",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_5eb2aa.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"male wolf\",\"hair\":\"thick gray fur\",\"eyes\":\"sharp yellow eyes\",\"skin\":\"fur-covered\",\"body_type\":\"large, muscular and lean build\",\"base_outfit\":\"none\",\"signature_items\":[\"sharp teeth\"]},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774102345269\",\"label\":\"趴下变成正常的狼\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"desc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774102345269\"}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"The Wolf launches fully out of the bed, claws stretched toward Little Red Riding Hood. For a split second, the room hangs in breathless silence between the Wolf’s next move and the girl’s desperate fear.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scd499f060a36940cdbaff3067267f0592\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Little Red Riding Hood freezes beside the wardrobe, unable to move as the beast bears down on her. Little Red Riding Hood remains trapped on the floor as the Wolf looms over her, the attack only moments from closing in.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc2b423517f56a4247bd9516d596c68481\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"A close-up catches her scream as she throws up her hands to protect herself.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc939b5ffaf31d403399743022e7576c5a\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"She falls hard onto the wooden floor, and her basket tips over, scattering pastries across the room.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"The Wolf lands heavily on all fours, claws scraping across the floorboards as it surges closer.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc7d21bf81e08d4179a8803b278a94ea28\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S6\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"From the floor, Little Red Riding Hood stares up in panic, breath shuddering in her chest.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc881264baa50940a5a494cd8e256a08d8\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Wolf launches fully out of the bed, claws stretched toward Little Red Riding Hood.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm orange and deep brown tones with high contrast between light and shadow.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Warm sunset light streams from the right side window, casting long dramatic shadows and highlighting the wolf's fur texture.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm orange and deep brown tones with high contrast between light and shadow.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground: Blurred dust motes dancing in a narrow band of light, soft focus wooden floor texture at the very bottom. Midground: The massive muscular Wolf dominates the center, suspended mid-air in a lunge, thick gray fur bristling, sharp claws extended forward towards the camera, occupying two-thirds of the frame. Background: The large wooden bed and open wardrobe are visible but slightly out of focus behind the wolf, deep shadows in the room corners. LightAndShadow: Warm sunset light streams from the right side window, casting long dramatic shadows and highlighting the wolf's fur texture. Hue: Warm orange and deep brown tones with high contrast between light and shadow.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B1_7b2c0b.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf flies forward through the air, claws extended at Little Red Riding Hood.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"A deep snarl and rushing movement fill the room.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E5-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btf2ef25c10c52409d9122e8a6dd67530e\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood freezes beside the wardrobe, unable to move as the beast bears down on her.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm red and cool shadow blues, creating a tense atmospheric contrast.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"The last ray of sunset cuts across the floor, illuminating her red cloak while her face remains partially in shadow.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm red and cool shadow blues, creating a tense atmospheric contrast.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground: Rough wooden floorboards in sharp focus at the bottom, scattered items blurred slightly. Midground: Little Red Riding Hood stands centrally, slim figure in white pinafore and red cloak, completely frozen, hands slightly raised, occupying the vertical center of the frame. Background: The open wooden wardrobe and the dark corner of the room behind her, a glimpse of the window with forest outline in the distance. LightAndShadow: The last ray of sunset cuts across the floor, illuminating her red cloak while her face remains partially in shadow. Hue: Warm red and cool shadow blues, creating a tense atmospheric contrast.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B2_1853ea.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood stands rooted beside the wardrobe, staring at the charging beast.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Only the scrape of claws and her shallow breathing can be heard.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E5-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btbaef377ad3cf46918b1fbbdca8338163\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"A close-up catches her scream as she throws up her hands to protect herself.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"High contrast warm skin tones against dark cool background, emphasizing urgency.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Strong side light from the right highlights the tears and sweat on her face, deep shadows on the left side of her face.\",\"Hue\":\"High contrast warm skin tones against dark cool background, emphasizing urgency.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground: Blurred edge of the wooden wardrobe on the left side, creating a sense of confinement. Midground: Little Red Riding Hood's upper body and face fill the frame, mouth wide open in a piercing scream, eyes shut tight, hands blurring as they fly up to shield her face. Background: The dark interior of the cottage is out of focus, only vague shapes of furniture visible. LightAndShadow: Strong side light from the right highlights the tears and sweat on her face, deep shadows on the left side of her face. Hue: High contrast warm skin tones against dark cool background, emphasizing urgency.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B3_ca836a.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Handheld\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood screams and throws up her hands in panic.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Her cry rings out sharply inside the cramped cottage.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E5-B3-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btb3ee51f7a65b433685c31bec8dc96a83\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"She falls hard onto the wooden floor, and her basket tips over, scattering pastries across the room.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Earthy browns of the floor and wood, punctuated by the bright red of the cloak and colorful basket contents.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"The warm light spot on the floor catches the falling objects, creating dynamic highlights as they move.\",\"Hue\":\"Earthy browns of the floor and wood, punctuated by the bright red of the cloak and colorful basket contents.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground: The rough texture of the wooden floorboards rushing up towards the lens. Midground: Little Red Riding Hood's body angled downwards as she hits the floor, red cloak spreading out, a woven basket tumbling beside her spilling apples and cloth. Background: The legs of the wooden bed and the base of the wardrobe visible at the top of the frame. LightAndShadow: The warm light spot on the floor catches the falling objects, creating dynamic highlights as they move. Hue: Earthy browns of the floor and wood, punctuated by the bright red of the cloak and colorful basket contents.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B4_efafd3.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood crashes to the floor and her basket spills open.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Pastries and cloth tumble across the creaking floorboards.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E5-B4-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt07522c8a39954e59b1c8809f05b679b6\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B6\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Wolf lands heavily on all fours, claws scraping across the floorboards as it surges closer.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Silhouette dark grays against the warm golden backlight, dramatic and threatening.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Sunset light backlights the wolf's fur, creating a rim light effect, while the underside is in deep shadow.\",\"Hue\":\"Silhouette dark grays against the warm golden backlight, dramatic and threatening.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground: Wood shavings and dust particles kicked up into the air, sharply focused near the lens. Midground: The Wolf lands heavily on all fours, muscular legs absorbing the impact, claws digging into the floorboards, jaws snapping shut on empty air, filling the lower half of the frame. Background: The spot where the girl just stood is now empty, the wooden bed and window visible in the distance. LightAndShadow: Sunset light backlights the wolf's fur, creating a rim light effect, while the underside is in deep shadow. Hue: Silhouette dark grays against the warm golden backlight, dramatic and threatening.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B5_99d6be.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf lands and surges forward with a violent scrape of claws.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Wood splinters and claws scrape harshly against the floor.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E5-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt6f5559c8f97744f398a0ddc6600fea0f\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B6\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B5\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B7\",\"BeatDesc\":\"From the floor, Little Red Riding Hood stares up in panic, breath shuddering in her chest.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Soft warm skin tones against the dark brown floor, intimate and vulnerable atmosphere.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft warm light illuminates her face from above, highlighting the fear in her eyes and the sweat on her forehead.\",\"Hue\":\"Soft warm skin tones against the dark brown floor, intimate and vulnerable atmosphere.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground: Blurred wooden floor texture in the immediate foreground, out of focus. Midground: Little Red Riding Hood's face lies on the floor, occupying the center, large round brown eyes staring up in absolute panic, cheeks pressed against the wood, chest heaving visibly. Background: The warm light spot on the floor extends behind her head, fading into the darker room. LightAndShadow: Soft warm light illuminates her face from above, highlighting the fear in her eyes and the sweat on her forehead. Hue: Soft warm skin tones against the dark brown floor, intimate and vulnerable atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B6_a5f9b8.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood lies on the floor, staring upward in helpless fear.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Her frightened breathing and the Wolf’s low growl fill the silence.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E5-B6-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btfd9728326d88444b8b9c5451ff56cd7a\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B7\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B6\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B8\",\"BeatDesc\":\"For a split second, the room hangs in breathless silence between the Wolf’s next move and the girl’s desperate fear.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"\",\"Hue\":\"\",\"Prompt\":\"\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B7_6f6009.png\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The confrontation seems to freeze for a heartbeat before the next burst of action.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Everything drops into a taut, breathless silence.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatUID\":\"bt5ff1d52fbf02447bb97b4ecf963cd032\",\"BeatType\":\"Pause\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Pause\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E5-B8\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E5-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E5-B7\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood remains trapped on the floor as the Wolf looms over her, the attack only moments from closing in.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"\",\"Hue\":\"\",\"Prompt\":\"Little Red Riding Hood, a slim girl clad in a white pinafore dress and a red hooded cloak, stands completely frozen in the path of the lunging beast.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B8_17a8e1.png\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf looms closer while Little Red Riding Hood remains cornered on the floor.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The beast’s breath sounds close and heavy in the dim room.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatUID\":\"bt8a5ffe8d46434bdc98ca4a8ea27f125a\",\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":true,\"contains_confrontation\":true,\"contains_revelation\":false,\"emotional_shift\":true}},{\"EventID\":\"S3-E1\",\"preEventID\":\"S3-E5\",\"nextEventID\":\"S3-E2\",\"EventDesc\":\"At that very moment, the cottage door burst open. A passing Huntsman charged in with his rifle and a thunderous shout, startling the wolf and giving Little Red Riding Hood a moment to escape.\",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\"],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774104228496\",\"label\":\"Beat S2-E2-B5 Variant\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_60fcb4.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774858379445\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_868bce.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，背影\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"id\":\"1774116366022\",\"label\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_75a39b.png\"],\"desc\":\"小红帽把红色斗篷带上了\",\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774164392741\",\"label\":\"同一角色\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\"],\"desc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，侧身，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"children\":[]},{\"id\":\"1774858829324\",\"label\":\"Variant 2\",\"images\":[],\"desc\":\"\",\"children\":[]}]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774858829324\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_5eb2aa.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"male wolf\",\"hair\":\"thick gray fur\",\"eyes\":\"sharp yellow eyes\",\"skin\":\"fur-covered\",\"body_type\":\"large, muscular and lean build\",\"base_outfit\":\"none\",\"signature_items\":[\"sharp teeth\"]},\"children\":[{\"id\":\"1774102345269\",\"label\":\"趴下变成正常的狼\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"desc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\\n\",\"children\":[]}]}],\"ActiveVersionID\":\"1774102345269\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Huntsman\",\"CharacterDesc\":{\"age_gender\":\"40-year-old man\",\"hair\":\"short dark hair\",\"eyes\":\"stern dark eyes\",\"skin\":\"weather-beaten skin\",\"body_type\":\"tall and muscular build\",\"base_outfit\":\"rugged leather hunting jacket and boots\",\"signature_items\":[\"hunting rifle\"]},\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Huntsman_885180.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Huntsman_885180.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"40-year-old man\",\"hair\":\"short dark hair\",\"eyes\":\"stern dark eyes\",\"skin\":\"weather-beaten skin\",\"body_type\":\"tall and muscular build\",\"base_outfit\":\"rugged leather hunting jacket and boots\",\"signature_items\":[\"hunting rifle\"]},\"children\":[]}]}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E1-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Pinned near the half-open door, Little Red Riding Hood clutches her basket and stumbles backward as danger closes around her.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sce60fa798d59142bf8857cb75ef5bd7d6\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E1-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"The Wolf turns from the bed toward Little Red Riding Hood, its body coiled aggressively in the dim cottage.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右