着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_14c06c.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood backs toward the door, clutching the basket to her chest.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The door creaks behind her as she retreats in panic.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E1-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btc6eeb63cae0a4641aa3076f723f39ded\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E1-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E1-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Wolf turns from the bed toward Little Red Riding Hood, its body coiled aggressively in the dim cottage.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Cool grays and dark browns.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Low Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Dim ambient light with subtle highlights on the wolf's fur, surrounded by heavy shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Cool grays and dark browns.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground shows the out-of-focus edge of a massive wooden wardrobe on the right. In the midground, the large muscular Wolf stands aggressively on all fours, facing left, its sharp teeth visible. The background reveals a wide wooden bed piled with thick bedding and a gridded glass window with the faint silhouette of a forest outside. The room's corners are filled with deep shadows. Faint natural light catches the Wolf's thick gray fur, establishing a tense and dangerous atmosphere in a crisp anime style.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E1-B2_4cc11d.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"趴下变成正常的狼，四肢着地\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf pivots inside the dim cottage and squares itself toward the girl.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Its low growl rumbles through the room.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E1-B2-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bta8b6c6cc7ede4a6db29e311abcd23d39\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E1-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E1-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The cottage door bursts open and the Huntsman appears in the doorway, gripping his rifle.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Earthy browns and stark contrasts.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reveal\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Strong backlight from the doorway outlining the Huntsman's silhouette against the dark room.\",\"Hue\":\"Earthy browns and stark contrasts.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features splintering wood particles and the violently swinging wooden door on the left. In the midground, the tall, muscular Huntsman fills the doorway, facing right, wearing a rugged leather hunting jacket and boots, gripping a long hunting rifle in both hands. The background shows the murky interior of the cottage. The sudden burst of action is highlighted by the dynamic contrast between the exterior light behind him and the dark interior. The overall tone is explosive and urgent, in a crisp anime style.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E1-B3_0cc3e7.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Huntsman\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '40-year-old man', 'hair': 'short dark hair', 'eyes': 'stern dark eyes', 'skin': 'weather-beaten skin', 'body_type': 'tall and muscular build', 'base_outfit': 'rugged leather hunting jacket and boots', 'signature_items': ['hunting rifle']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Huntsman_885180.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Handheld\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The door flies open and the Huntsman storms into the doorway with his rifle.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The door slams hard against the wall as boots pound across the threshold.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reveal\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E1-B3-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btaad8760be9ef4fcfbacaa339582658ec\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E1-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E1-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Huntsman charges inside and raises the rifle directly at the Wolf.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm browns and metallic grays.\",\"BeatPurpose