ks in place, shocked by the Huntsman’s sudden arrival.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Its growl catches off into a tense silence.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E1-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt7eba3c4681174403bf2905228c37c55e\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E1-B6\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E1-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E1-B5\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood presses herself against the rough doorframe, shocked but sensing rescue has arrived.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm orange, red, and deep black.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"A stark beam of warm light across the character's face, contrasting sharply with the pitch-black background.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm orange, red, and deep black.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features the out-of-focus rough texture of the wooden doorframe on the left edge. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood's face and shoulders fill the frame, her large round brown eyes wide with sudden shock, pulling a woven basket tightly against her white pinafore dress. The background is completely blurred out into dark, indistinct cottage shadows. A warm beam of fading dusk light clearly illuminates her pale, frightened face. The mood is tense and fearful, in a crisp anime style.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E1-B6_e28509.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，