"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E2-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E2-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Huntsman lunges forward and strikes the Wolf with the heavy stock of his rifle.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm orange and deep brown.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"High contrast, warm directional sunset light from the right side cutting through shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm orange and deep brown.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features the blurred edge of a wooden table, emphasizing the sudden movement. In the midground, the tall, muscular Huntsman in a rugged leather jacket lunges forward, occupying the center of the frame, thrusting his hunting rifle downwards with an intense, focused expression. The background shows the dimly lit cottage interior with scattered debris on the floor. Warm sunset light cuts across the room from the right, highlighting the dust kicked up by the struggle, creating a tense, high-contrast atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B1_288b84.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Huntsman\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '40-year-old man', 'hair': 'short dark hair', 'eyes': 'stern dark eyes', 'skin': 'weather-beaten skin', 'body_type': 'tall and muscular build', 'base_outfit': 'rugged leather hunting jacket and boots', 'signature_items': ['hunting rifle']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Huntsman_885180.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Huntsman throws his weight forward and slams the rifle stock down toward the Wolf.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"A heavy impact cracks through the room.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E2-B1-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt218a016d7e784326bc2f70022f903118\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E2-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E2-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Wolf is driven to the floor, snarling helplessly as the Huntsman pins it down.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Muted gray and warm amber.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Harsh, narrow beam of warm light highlighting the Wolf's face against dark shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Muted gray and warm amber.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground shows the blurred, dark metal barrel of the hunting rifle pressing down diagonally. In the midground, the large gray Wolf lies pinned against the rough wooden floorboards, filling the frame with its bared sharp teeth and bristling fur, its sharp yellow eyes glaring upward. The background is a dark, out-of-focus wooden floor. A stark, narrow beam of sunset light hits the Wolf's snarling face, highlighting the textures of its fur against the deep shadows of the floor.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B2_077295.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/