emains a dark abyss.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B5_b06ab2.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Huntsman\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '40-year-old man', 'hair': 'short dark hair', 'eyes': 'stern dark eyes', 'skin': 'weather-beaten skin', 'body_type': 'tall and muscular build', 'base_outfit': 'rugged leather hunting jacket and boots', 'signature_items': ['hunting rifle']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Huntsman_885180.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Huntsman stands before the open wardrobe and peers inside.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Only a faint rustle comes from within the dark wardrobe.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Environment\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E4\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E2-B5-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt2776fed2c06241549e4fd898aef5a08d\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E2-B6\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E2-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B5\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B7\",\"BeatDesc\":\"From the Huntsman’s point of view, the inside of the wardrobe is a narrow, shadowy space crowded with hanging clothes.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Near black and faint warm brown.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Environment\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Extremely low key lighting, mostly pitch black with faint, warm rim light on the coats.\",\"Hue\":\"Near black and faint warm brown.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features the blurred wooden edges of the wardrobe door frame. In the midground, the dark, shadowy interior of the wardrobe fills the frame, with faint, indistinguishable shapes of hanging coats barely visible in the gloom. The background is entirely consumed by the pitch-black depths of the closet. Only a faint sliver of warm ambient light spills over the edges of the coats, creating an eerie, suspenseful, and claustrophobic atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B6_249776.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The camera peers into the cramped darkness of the wardrobe.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Fabric rustles softly in the enclosed dark.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Environment\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E4\",\"ShotIndex\":2,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E2-B5-S2\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btc47bd1bc07bf450bb3f798e99f2a3f7e\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E2-B7\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E2-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B6\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B8\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Curled among the coats, the real Grandmother is revealed inside the wardrobe, frightened but unharmed.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm golden skin tones contrasting with cool dark shadows.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reveal\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Chiaroscuro effect, a single sharp beam of warm light hitting the face surrounded by deep shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm golden skin tones contrasting with cool dark shadows.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground consists of blurred, dark fabric of hanging coats framing the shot. In the midground, the frail 70-year-old Grandmother in a white traditional nightgown is huddled in the center, her white-gray hair messy, squinting her kind blue eyes against the light. The background is the dark wooden back panel of the wardrobe. A sudden, sharp beam of warm sunset light cuts across her face, illuminating her wrinkled features against the surrounding darkness, creating a dramatic reveal.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B7_706347.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '70-year-old woman', 'hair': 'white gray hair', 'eyes': 'kind blue eyes', 'skin': 'wrinkled fair skin', 'body_type': 'frail, small frame', 'base_outfit': 'traditional nightgown', 'signature_items': ['thick blankets']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":28,\"width\":26,\"height\":58,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Grandmother is discovered huddled inside the wardrobe among the hanging coats.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"A small frightened breath breaks from the darkness.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Reveal\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E2\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E2-B6-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt5ceba7e3cdfa4c7da977deb4a7ac055f\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E2-B8\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E2-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B7\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B9\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The Huntsman helps Grandmother out of the wardrobe and brings her back into the room.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm amber and soft brown.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Balanced warm lighting filling the previously dark space, soft shadows.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm amber and soft brown.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground shows the blurred back of the Huntsman's shoulder on the left. In the midground, the open wardrobe reveals the frail Grandmother huddled inside, looking up in surprise, occupying the right side of the frame. The background shows the dimly lit interior of the cottage behind the wardrobe. The warm sunset light spills fully into the wardrobe now, washing over the Grandmother and connecting the two characters in a shared space of relief.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B8_87f268.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '40-year-old man', 'hair': 'short dark hair', 'eyes': 'stern dark eyes', 'skin': 'weather-beaten skin', 'body_type': 'tall and muscular build', 'base_outfit': 'rugged leather hunting jacket and boots', 'signature_items': ['hunting rifle']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":34,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Huntsman\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '70-year-old woman', 'hair': 'white gray hair', 'eyes': 'kind blue eyes', 'skin': 'wrinkled fair skin', 'body_type': 'frail, small frame', 'base_outfit': 'traditional nightgown', 'signature_items': ['thick blankets']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Huntsman_885180.png\",\"x\":66,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly Out\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Huntsman steadies Grandmother and helps her step out of the wardrobe.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Their movements are slow and careful over the creaking floor.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E2\",\"ShotIndex\":2,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E2-B6-S2\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt0f17a77112e04dc0a0ac7c7259c90a15\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E2-B9\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E2-S7\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B8\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E2-B10\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood’s face fills with relief as she realizes her grandmother is alive.\",\"BeatAtmosphere\":\"Warm peach, vibrant red, and soft brown.\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft, flattering warm light on the face, creating bright catchlights in the eyes.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm peach, vibrant red, and soft brown.\",\"Prompt\":\"Foreground features a slight blur of dust motes dancing in the air. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood's face is centered, her large round brown eyes filled with tears of relief, her mouth open in a gasp, wearing her white pinafore dress and red hooded cloak. The background is the soft, out-of-focus wooden wall of the cottage. Soft, warm sunset light illuminates her face evenly, highlighting the moisture in her eyes and creating a tender, highly emotional atmosphere.\",\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B9_f4aa5f.png\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"\",\"LocationName\":\"\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"