画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"{'age_gender': '70-year-old woman', 'hair': 'white gray hair', 'eyes': 'kind blue eyes', 'skin': 'wrinkled fair skin', 'body_type': 'frail, small frame', 'base_outfit': 'traditional nightgown', 'signature_items': ['thick blankets']}\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":34,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":66,\"y\":30,\"width\":24,\"height\":56,\"Rotation\":\"\",\"Posture\":\"\"}],\"Animation\":{\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[],\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Grandmother steps toward Little Red Riding Hood and pulls her into her arms.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The room softens into quiet sobs and relieved breathing.\",\"dialogueList\":[]},\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"ExpandRule\":\"E5\",\"ShotIndex\":1,\"ShotID\":\"S3-E2-B8-S1\",\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\"}],\"AnalysisTags\":{\"contains_violence\":true,\"contains_confrontation\":true,\"contains_revelation\":true,\"emotional_shift\":false}},{\"EventID\":\"S3-E3\",\"preEventID\":\"S3-E2\",\"nextEventID\":\"\",\"EventDesc\":\"Safe at last, Little Red Riding Hood rushed into Grandmother's arms. As the wolf lay defeated on the floor, warm sunset light broke through the cottage window and filled the room with relief.\",\"EventCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"Characte