\",\"base_outfit\":\"traditional nightgown\",\"signature_items\":[\"thick blankets\"]},\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"],\"CharacterVersionTree\":[{\"id\":\"root\",\"label\":\"Main\",\"images\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"],\"desc\":{\"age_gender\":\"70-year-old woman\",\"hair\":\"white gray hair\",\"eyes\":\"kind blue eyes\",\"skin\":\"wrinkled fair skin\",\"body_type\":\"frail, small frame\",\"base_outfit\":\"traditional nightgown\",\"signature_items\":[\"thick blankets\"]},\"children\":[]}]}],\"EventLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"ScriptList\":[{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"],\"Type\":\"Presentation\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"The defeated Wolf lies bound on the cottage floor, no longer able to threaten anyone.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scc970da36b1dc421f84f1381ca60a74b1\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S2\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Little Red Riding Hood pulls back slightly from Grandmother, her face still wet with tears and relief.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc58121620435449e78ad5f01eb6dbe9ae\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Dialogue\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Over Grandmother’s shoulder, Little Red Riding Hood looks up, still shaken, as if confirming that the nightmare is truly over.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scc71b6213562246cc9a9505699d22d091\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S4\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Grandmother looks down at her gently, her lined face softening with reassurance.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc12e9e4cde5b847d7ae1e08e6e1d39d95\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Dialogue\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Grandmother speaks softly to comfort the frightened girl.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"scd296622a759145d2802a5173ed294249\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S6\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"Type\":\"Action\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Unable to hold back her feelings any longer, Little Red Riding Hood throws herself fully into Grandmother’s arms. The camera lingers on their tight embrace as Little Red Riding Hood buries her face against Grandmother and cries.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sced6a141f92c94868bdf467cb66370ca1\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S7\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"],\"Type\":\"Reaction\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"Grandmother wraps her thin arms around the girl and holds her close in quiet relief.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sccd0291e838434c19bb0c2cae1141b95a\"},{\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S8\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"],\"Type\":\"Reveal\",\"Actant\":{\"Action\":\"A warm shaft of sunset light breaks through the cottage window and falls across the reunited pair. The camera pulls back to reveal the whole cottage bathed in golden light, ending the scene in peace and safety.\"},\"Space\":{\"Environment\":\"Grandmother's cottage\"},\"Focalization\":\"External\",\"ScriptUID\":\"sc169e9a94eadc41f294f0699834238565\"}],\"BeatList\":[{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B1\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S1\",\"preBeatID\":\"\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B2\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The defeated Wolf lies bound on the cottage floor, no longer able to threaten anyone.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Dim, moody lighting with a sharp shaft of cool light spilling from the half-open door, casting deep, dramatic shadows across the rough floorboards.\",\"Hue\":\"A somber palette dominated by the deep, shadowy browns of the wood and the steely, cool grays of the wolf's fur.\",\"Prompt\":\"The blurred edge of a half-open wooden door creates a framing foreground. In the midground, occupying the lower half of the frame, a large, muscular gray wolf lies defeated on scattered wooden floorboards, tightly bound by thick ropes. The background is a dim, shadow-draped corner of the rustic room. A shaft of cool light spills through the doorway, casting harsh contrasts on the rough wood texture and the wolf's fur, creating a somber atmosphere with deep browns and cool grays.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C3\",\"CharacterName\":\"Wolf\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\",\"x\":20,\"y\":50,\"width\":60,\"height\":40,\"Rotation\":\"Lying on its side, slightly angled towards the camera\",\"Posture\":\"Lying defeated, tightly bound with thick ropes\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B1_185a61.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The Wolf lies tied up on the floor, spent and unable to move.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Only the subdued sound of its rough breathing remains.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt3d264074d9ea461dbf2fd8a423eafa48\",\"BeatType\":\"Presentation\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Presentation\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B2\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S2\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B1\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B3\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Little Red Riding Hood pulls back slightly from Grandmother, her face still wet with tears and relief.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft, warm directional light gently falls on her face from above, catching the moisture of her tears and creating a tender, glowing highlight against the darker room.\",\"Hue\":\"A warm, emotional palette highlighting the vibrant red of her hood and the golden, cozy browns of the cottage interior.\",\"Prompt\":\"In the foreground, the blurred edge of a large wooden bed and soft quilts frame the bottom of the shot. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood kneels by the bed, occupying the center of the frame, leaning back slightly with her tear-stained face tilted upward, her large brown eyes looking up. The background features the softly lit rustic wooden walls of the cottage. Warm directional light falls from above onto her face, illuminating her tears, with an overall warm color palette dominated by reddish-browns and golden yellows, creating a tender and emotional atmosphere.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":30,\"y\":20,\"width\":40,\"height\":60,\"Rotation\":\"Facing forward, head tilted upward\",\"Posture\":\"Kneeling on the floor, leaning back slightly\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B2_298d95.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood leans back from the embrace, still crying with relief.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Her breathing is unsteady, but the danger has passed.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btb9a213856381445ca1c75c28f7cc2019\",\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B3\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S3\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B2\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B4\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Over Grandmother’s shoulder, Little Red Riding Hood looks up, still shaken, as if confirming that the nightmare is truly over.\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Over-the-Shoulder\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Faint warm candlelight and cool moonlight shining through the window meet in the room, forming a soft side light that outlines a clear boundary between light and shadow on Little Red Riding Hood's cheek, amplifying her uneasy micro-expressions.\",\"Hue\":\"Dominated by a deep, cold, and gloomy blue tone, with Little Red Riding Hood's scarlet cloak and pure white nightgown acting as the visual focus, creating a strong color contrast and emotional tension.\",\"Prompt\":\"In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood is positioned slightly off-center to the left, occupying about half the height. She looks slightly up and to the right, hands tightly gripping her white nightgown, with her red cloak draped over her shoulders. The background is the interior of Grandmother's rustic wooden cottage, with details of old furniture hidden in heavy shadows. A beam of cold moonlight intertwines with faint warm yellow candlelight, striking Little Red Riding Hood's face from the side. The overall color palette presents a gloomy blue tone with highly contrasting red.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":35,\"y\":50,\"width\":40,\"height\":55,\"Rotation\":\"Looking Up-Right\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, clutching nightgown\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":85,\"y\":65,\"width\":30,\"height\":70,\"Rotation\":\"Back to camera\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, out of focus foreground\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B3_c1e52d.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood looks up from the embrace, still trembling as she speaks softly.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Her voice is small and shaky in the quiet aftermath.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S3-E3-S3-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\",\"Line\":\"Grandmother...\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Young, timid but clear girl voice\"}],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt599e600fea8c4e3287cb4a70c04143ee\",\"BeatType\":\"Dialogue\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Dialogue\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B4\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S4\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B3\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B5\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Grandmother looks down at her gently, her lined face softening with reassurance.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"\",\"Hue\":\"\",\"Prompt\":\"\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":65.2,\"y\":29.6,\"width\":45,\"height\":65,\"Rotation\":\"Looking Down-Left\",\"Posture\":\"Leaning forward slightly, hands reaching out\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":36.2,\"y\":42.2,\"width\":35,\"height\":40,\"Rotation\":\"Back to camera\",\"Posture\":\"Standing, out of focus foreground\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B4_a511bf.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Grandmother gazes down with deep relief and tenderness.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The room is quiet except for calm, steady breathing.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"reuse\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt35052e6f605c4c61999368c6736e2b37\",\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B5\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S5\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B4\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B6\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Grandmother speaks softly to comfort the frightened girl.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"\",\"Hue\":\"\",\"Prompt\":\"\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":48.3,\"y\":15.8,\"width\":35,\"height\":70,\"Rotation\":\"0\",\"Posture\":\"Back facing the camera, shoulders relaxed\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":73.3,\"y\":25.3,\"width\":45,\"height\":60,\"Rotation\":\"0\",\"Posture\":\"Sitting on the bed, face turned towards the left, smiling\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B5_090041.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Static\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Grandmother answers with a warm, reassuring smile.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Her voice is frail but comforting.\",\"dialogueList\":[{\"DialogueID\":\"S3-E3-S5-D1\",\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_30d84e.png\",\"Line\":\"It’s all right now, my dear.\",\"VoiceSettings\":\"Young, timid but clear girl voice\"}],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"reuse\",\"BeatUID\":\"btbf52751230d244a49f5988f4e8ab8daa\",\"BeatType\":\"Dialogue\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Dialogue\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B6\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B5\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B7\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Unable to hold back her feelings any longer, Little Red Riding Hood throws herself fully into Grandmother’s arms.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Side-backlighting outlines the silhouette of Little Red Riding Hood's forward-leaning motion, the edges of her cloak shimmering faintly, while the warm light from the fireplace in the background provides a sense of depth and layering.\",\"Hue\":\"The highly saturated color of the red cloak forms a strong visual contrast with the surrounding dark brown and dark orange environment, highlighting the emotional outburst.\",\"Prompt\":\"No obvious foreground obstruction. In the midground, Little Red Riding Hood abruptly leans forward on the left side of the frame, her arms eagerly reaching out, her bright red cloak flying back with the motion. On the right, Grandmother sits on the bed, opening her arms to welcome her. The background is the dim but cozy depths of the cottage, with the residual light of the fireplace flickering on the firewood in the background, offering clear spatial perspective.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":35,\"y\":50,\"width\":40,\"height\":75,\"Rotation\":\"15\",\"Posture\":\"Leaning heavily forward, arms reaching out\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":80,\"y\":50,\"width\":35,\"height\":65,\"Rotation\":\"0\",\"Posture\":\"Sitting upright on the bed, arms slightly open to welcome\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B6_edcca0.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Handheld\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Little Red Riding Hood rushes forward again and embraces Grandmother tightly.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The sudden movement breaks into sobs of relief.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bte272c7ba501346b3bdfcccb12ba452c1\",\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B7\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S6\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B6\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B8\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera lingers on their tight embrace as Little Red Riding Hood buries her face against Grandmother and cries.\",\"ShotSize\":\"CU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"A soft spotlight strikes precisely on Little Red Riding Hood's side profile, highlighting the reflection of her tears and the texture of her skin. The surrounding environment sinks into soft darkness, creating an emotional spotlight effect.\",\"Hue\":\"Warm skin tones, the bright red hood, and the simple nightgown interweave, while the background blurs into a deep warm brown, creating an atmosphere that is emotionally intense yet full of security.\",\"Prompt\":\"The fabric of Grandmother's nightgown with its delicate floral pattern occupies the right half of the frame as a midground anchor. Little Red Riding Hood's face is pressed tightly against the soft fabric, occupying the center-left of the frame, with crystal-clear teardrops sliding down her young cheek. The background is completely blurred into warm brown and orange patches, with the light precisely focused on the tearful face.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":45,\"y\":55,\"width\":60,\"height\":80,\"Rotation\":\"0\",\"Posture\":\"Face buried in the fabric, eyes tightly closed and crying\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":85,\"y\":50,\"width\":50,\"height\":90,\"Rotation\":\"0\",\"Posture\":\"Body and nightgown occupying the right side of the frame, embracing Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B7_ade4cd.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"The embrace tightens as Little Red Riding Hood buries her face into Grandmother’s chest.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Soft crying and rustling fabric fill the room.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"btb07203caed4c4f30882fb915d428a5b5\",\"BeatType\":\"Action\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Action\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B8\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S7\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B7\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B9\",\"BeatDesc\":\"Grandmother wraps her thin arms around the girl and holds her close in quiet relief.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MCU\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Soft, diffused indoor lighting with faint shadows, creating an intimate and slightly sentimental atmosphere.\",\"Hue\":\"A warm but slightly dim indoor color palette, forming a strong visual contrast between the taupe of Grandmother's clothing and the bright red of Little Red Riding Hood.\",\"Prompt\":\"The blurred edge of a wooden chair back forms a slight foreground obstruction at the bottom of the frame. In the midground, Grandmother, with her eyes closed, gently rests her chin on Little Red Riding Hood's bright red hood, her arms tightly embracing the girl's back, occupying about two-thirds of the central area. The background features blurred wooden cabin walls and faint shadows. Soft diffused light outlines their silhouettes, and the overall color tone presents a warm, dark palette with reddish-brown hues.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":50,\"y\":45,\"width\":60,\"height\":80,\"Rotation\":\"0\",\"Posture\":\"Hugging Little Red Riding Hood, eyes closed, chin resting on the red hood.\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":50,\"y\":60,\"width\":45,\"height\":50,\"Rotation\":\"180\",\"Posture\":\"Being hugged, back facing the camera, trembling.\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B8_bfc7a3.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly In\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Grandmother gently cradles Little Red Riding Hood and holds her close.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"The moment settles into a fragile, peaceful silence.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt62901d1f929a4167aa75f9e412fbe088\",\"BeatType\":\"Reaction\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reaction\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B9\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S8\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B8\",\"nextBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B10\",\"BeatDesc\":\"A warm shaft of sunset light breaks through the cottage window and falls across the reunited pair.\",\"ShotSize\":\"MS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"Eye Level\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"Strong directional light shoots in from the window, forming a clear light beam and high-contrast illuminated areas and shadows, with floating dust faintly visible in the beam.\",\"Hue\":\"Brilliant gold and warm orange-red dominate the frame, breaking the previous gloom and bringing a strong sense of hope.\",\"Prompt\":\"The heavy wooden edge of the window frame forms a natural visual leading line in the right foreground. In the midground, the embracing Grandmother and Little Red Riding Hood turn slightly sideways, fully illuminated by a bright beam of golden sunset light, occupying about half the height on the left side of the frame. The background is a paned glass window, outside of which parting heavy clouds are faintly visible. A strong warm golden light beam slants into the frame from the right, forming a clear band of light in the air. The overall color tone is filled with a divine warm orange.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":40,\"y\":50,\"width\":35,\"height\":65,\"Rotation\":\"-45\",\"Posture\":\"Hugging Little Red Riding Hood, bathed in sunlight.\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":40,\"y\":65,\"width\":25,\"height\":40,\"Rotation\":\"135\",\"Posture\":\"Being hugged, bathed in sunlight.\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B9_2b47e5.png\",\"Animation\":{\"CameraMove\":\"Dolly Out\",\"SubjectMove\":\"Sunset light suddenly pours through the window and onto the reunited pair.\",\"BackgroundVoice\":\"Wind stirs softly outside as the light breaks through.\",\"dialogueList\":[],\"BeatVideoUrl\":\"\",\"VideoUrl\":[]},\"FrameMode\":\"generate\",\"BeatUID\":\"bt8fc9616c80c14f27a74c6da291c37078\",\"BeatType\":\"Reveal\",\"BeatPurpose\":\"Reveal\"},{\"BeatID\":\"S3-E3-B10\",\"ScriptID\":\"S3-E3-S8\",\"preBeatID\":\"S3-E3-B9\",\"nextBeatID\":\"\",\"BeatDesc\":\"The camera pulls back to reveal the whole cottage bathed in golden light, ending the scene in peace and safety.\",\"ShotSize\":\"WS\",\"CameraPosition\":\"High Angle\",\"LightAndShadow\":\"The broad afterglow of the sunset fills the entire room, with an extremely obvious Tyndall effect; the slanting beams of light are clearly visible amidst the dust in the air.\",\"Hue\":\"Rich amber and golden yellow interweave, while the shadows present a deep warm brown, creating an ultimate sense of warmth and redemption.\",\"Prompt\":\"A floor scattered with hay and a rustic wooden table form a broad and slightly blurred foreground. In the midground, the grandmother and granddaughter embrace tightly in the center of the room; their figures appear relatively small in the vast space, occupying about one-fourth of the frame's height. The background reveals the rough fireplace deep within the wooden cottage and towering wooden beams. The huge paned window lets in brilliant sunset light, and clear golden Tyndall rays pierce through the entire room, enveloping all the furnishings in a rich amber and golden glow.\",\"BeatLocation\":{\"LocationID\":\"L3\",\"LocationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"LocationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"},\"BeatCharacters\":[{\"CharacterID\":\"C5\",\"CharacterName\":\"Grandmother\",\"CharacterImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\",\"x\":45,\"y\":60,\"width\":15,\"height\":35,\"Rotation\":\"-45\",\"Posture\":\"Standing and hugging the young girl in the center of the room.\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"},{\"CharacterID\":\"C1\",\"CharacterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"CharacterImageURL\":[],\"x\":45,\"y\":68,\"width\":10,\"height\":20,\"Rotation\":\"135\",\"Posture\":\"Embraced by the grandmother.\",\"CharacterDesc\":\"\"}],\"FrameImageURL\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E3-B10_587ed3.png\",\"Animation\":