\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-scfd34b00df43f4e0c9a85f77ae93d97d4\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S1-E2-bt83e83de2473349ff96a58fd490823f2f\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S1-E2-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt83e83de2473349ff96a58fd490823f2f\",\"scriptUid\":\"scfd34b00df43f4e0c9a85f77ae93d97d4\",\"videoUrl\":\"\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B5_a806ce.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S1-E2-bt83e83de2473349ff96a58fd490823f2f\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S1-E2-B5\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E2-B5_a806ce.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood's garden\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Little_Red_Riding_Hood_s_garden_dc1354.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S1-E2-scfd34b00df43f4e0c9a85f77ae93d97d4\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"script-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"type\":\"script-wrapper\",\"position\":{\"x\":42.205924223933835,\"y\":83.62764637836062},\"data\":{\"scriptId\":\"S2-E1-S1\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"width\":1088,\"height\":612},\"parentNode\":\"group-bg-S2-E1\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d-C1\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":184},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"locationId\":\"L2\",\"locationName\":\"Forest path\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B1_a879ed.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S2-E1-bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"videoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B1_ba08dacae5c4443ca86ede7ff0a23798.mp4\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B1_a879ed.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-bt2d2a817ab6fd4c3da00f39c0153bea95\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S2-E1-B1\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B1_a879ed.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc358555ba764544489f9d0c8cce9d6f9d\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"script-S2-E1-sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"type\":\"script-wrapper\",\"position\":{\"x\":1156.5980252586878,\"y\":104.0394948262292},\"data\":{\"scriptId\":\"S2-E1-S2\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"width\":1088,\"height\":612},\"parentNode\":\"group-bg-S2-E1\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S2-E1-sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe-C1\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":184},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"beatUid\":\"bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S2-E1-sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"beatUid\":\"bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"locationId\":\"L2\",\"locationName\":\"Forest path\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"beatUid\":\"bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B2_06800b.png\",\"frameMode\":\"reuse\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S2-E1-bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"beatUid\":\"bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc29b12be372b14dc9a2c7dead129a7dbe\",\"videoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B2_3c571293bfca41ce8690acb7e9eda193.mp4\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B2_06800b.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-bt1dc596a770af4190a79d4061ea031435\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S2-E1-B2\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B2_06800b.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6