fc0d4a31a479f979a48ce8b0bd858\",\"scriptUid\":\"sceac8904d2ab84a23a1ff32f76eba42f0\",\"videoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B4_6ae93554e41f43c1aa655b3c9ce44dce.mp4\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B4_bb19f3.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-btf67fc0d4a31a479f979a48ce8b0bd858\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S2-E1-B4\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B4_bb19f3.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C3\",\"name\":\"Wolf\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Wolf_bd35a1.png\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-sceac8904d2ab84a23a1ff32f76eba42f0\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"script-S2-E1-scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"type\":\"script-wrapper\",\"position\":{\"x\":4544,\"y\":100.63752008491792},\"data\":{\"scriptId\":\"S2-E1-S5\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"width\":1088,\"height\":612},\"parentNode\":\"group-bg-S2-E1\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S2-E1-scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3-C1\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":184},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S2-E1-scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"locationId\":\"L2\",\"locationName\":\"Forest path\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B5_910b31.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E1-scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S2-E1-bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd75f7e6566f749fabc1770ca954233a3\",\"videoUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/Video/S2-E1-B5_7284eb59c5a248298f8fa0df5f4a3eab.mp4\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B5_910b31.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E1-bt902821a025ad4fb9987d39a10209ba83\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S2-E1-B5\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E1-B5_910b31.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"