":77.5,\"y\":272},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E5-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\",\"scriptUid\":\"sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\",\"locationId\":\"L2\",\"locationName\":\"Forest path\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用对角线构图，一条蜿蜒的土路从画面右下角向左上角延伸，形成强烈的视觉引导线。[前景描述] 画面右下角是粗壮的橡树树根和几簇随风摇曳的野花，左下角有几只翩翩起舞的蝴蝶。[中景主体及方位] 画面中央是一棵高耸入云的巨大橡树，占据了大部分视野，树旁有一条铺满落叶的分岔小径。[背景深度] 背景是层层叠叠的茂密树冠和森林深处，雾气在树干间隐约可见，拉伸了空间深度。[光影效果] 阳光透过繁密的树冠从正上方滤下，形成一道道清晰的丁达尔光柱，在林间小路上洒下斑驳的光影，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E5-sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E5-bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E5-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\",\"scriptUid\":\"sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B5_3171da.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E5-sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S2-E5-bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S2-E5-B5\",\"beatUid\":\"bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\",\"scriptUid\":\"sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\",\"videoUrl\":\"\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B5_3171da.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S2-E5-bt4967d3014a4d468fb03d23df0e87a9da\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S2-E5-B5\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E5-B5_3171da.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L2\",\"name\":\"Forest path\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Forest_path_ee6bca.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S2-E5-sca98eb678f1c145b39479188d4b0955b0\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"script-S3-E4-scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"type\":\"script-wrapper\",\"position\":{\"x\":20.094492887520346,\"y\":99.49603793322513},\"data\":{\"scriptId\":\"S3-E4-S1\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"width\":1088,\"height\":612},\"parentNode\":\"group-bg-S3-E4\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S3-E4-scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1-C1\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":184},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E4-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt0efd57ed08da4c069c8250b6c84ef099\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E4-scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S3-E4-scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E4-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt0efd57ed08da4c069c8250b6c84ef099\",\"scriptUid\":\"scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"locationId\":\"L3\",\"locationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E4-scd1cb35eadcb34cd8972299fff76c9ab1\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S3-E4-bt0efd57ed08da4c069c8250b6c84ef099\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\