criptUid\":\"scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，特写（面部）构图，平视，温暖的微笑，双手向上举起，面朝自己的行动方向，手持编织篮，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E5-scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S3-E5-scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":360},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E5-B4\",\"beatUid\":\"bt07522c8a39954e59b1c8809f05b679b6\",\"scriptUid\":\"scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"locationId\":\"L3\",\"locationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E5-scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S3-E5-bt07522c8a39954e59b1c8809f05b679b6\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E5-B4\",\"beatUid\":\"bt07522c8a39954e59b1c8809f05b679b6\",\"scriptUid\":\"scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E5-B4_efafd3.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L3\",\"name\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E5-scc28281ceba134dd1acd6e7b5b628fd5e\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S3-E5-bt07522c8a39954e59b1c8809f05b679b6\",\"type\":\"vi