]}\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc-C1\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":272},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E2-B10\",\"beatUid\":\"bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"characterId\":\"C1\",\"characterName\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"characterImageURL\":\"\",\"characterDesc\":\"同一角色，中景（半身）构图，平视，表情自信，放下双手转身向前迈步，手中提着篮子，面朝自己的行动方向，卡通新海诚动漫风格，保持角色设计一致，背景颜色RGB（0，255，0）\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-loc-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"type\":\"location-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":448},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E2-B10\",\"beatUid\":\"bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"locationId\":\"L3\",\"locationName\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"locationImageURL\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\",\"locationDesc\":\"[构图布局] 采用框景构图，通过一扇半开的破旧木门向屋内延伸视线。[前景描述] 画面左下角是半开的木门边缘和粗糙的木纹，右下角是散落着几件杂物的老旧木地板。[中景主体及方位] 画面正中央是一张宽大的木制床铺，床上堆着厚厚的被褥，旁边有一个打开的巨大木制衣橱。[背景深度] 房间深处是一扇带有格栅的玻璃窗，窗外隐约可见森林的轮廓，屋内角落布满阴影。[光影效果] 最后一缕黄昏的夕阳从右侧窗户斜射进来，在床铺和地板上投下狭长的暖色光斑，与屋内的幽暗形成对比，整体呈现卡通新海诚风格，线条清晰，明亮的自然光。\"},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-frame-S3-E2-bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"type\":\"first-frame-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":306.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E2-B10\",\"beatUid\":\"bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"frameImageUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B10_e05545.png\",\"frameMode\":\"generate\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"shotSize\":\"\",\"cameraPosition\":\"\",\"lightAndShadow\":\"\",\"hue\":\"\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C5\",\"name\":\"Grandmother\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"},{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L3\",\"name\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-video-S3-E2-bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"type\":\"video-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":740.5,\"y\":214.5},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E2-B10\",\"beatUid\":\"bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"scriptUid\":\"sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"videoUrl\":\"\",\"thumbnailUrl\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B10_e05545.png\",\"duration\":\"\",\"isGenerating\":false,\"connectedFrameId\":\"pipeline-frame-S3-E2-bt841d86f6dfd94f47a7b7f4092f0b4dec\",\"connectedBeatId\":\"S3-E2-B10\",\"connectedFrameImage\":\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S3-E2-B10_e05545.png\",\"connectedCharacters\":[{\"id\":\"C5\",\"name\":\"Grandmother\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_b0246c.png\"},{\"id\":\"C1\",\"name\":\"Little Red Riding Hood\",\"image\":\"\"}],\"connectedLocation\":{\"id\":\"L3\",\"name\":\"Grandmother's cottage\",\"image\":\"/RefImage/Grandmother_s_cottage_ea6f7a.png\"}},\"parentNode\":\"script-S3-E2-sc035031698a714cb79f4e88ef780c2ebc\",\"extent\":\"parent\"},{\"id\":\"script-S3-E3-scc970da36b1dc421f84f1381ca60a74b1\",\"type\":\"script-wrapper\",\"position\":{\"x\":28.031497629173373,\"y\":87.5905308207457},\"data\":{\"scriptId\":\"S3-E3-S1\",\"scriptUid\":\"scc970da36b1dc421f84f1381ca60a74b1\",\"width\":1088,\"height\":612},\"parentNode\":\"group-bg-S3-E3\"},{\"id\":\"pipeline-char-S3-E3-scc970da36b1dc421f84f1381ca60a74b1-C3\",\"type\":\"character-card-node\",\"position\":{\"x\":77.5,\"y\":184},\"data\":{\"beatId\":\"S3-E3-B1\",\"beatUid\":\"bt3d264074d9ea461dbf2fd8a423eafa48\",\"scriptUid\":\"scc970da36b1dc421f84f1381ca60a74b1\",\"characterId\":\"C3\",\"characterName\":\"Wolf\",\"characterImageURL\":\"