\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \"The wolf threw off the blankets and lunged. Little Red Riding Hood screamed and fell to the floor.\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E1\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"猎人冲入制止狼\", \"color\": \"#0000FF\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \"At that very moment, the door burst open. A passing \"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"bold\"}, {\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"characterMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"1774073001914\", \"title\": \"Character\", \"note\": \"huntsman\"}}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E1\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"猎人冲入制止狼\", \"color\": \"#0000FF\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \"huntsman\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E1\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"猎人冲入制止狼\", \"color\": \"#0000FF\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \" charged in with his rifle and a thundering shout that stopped the \"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"bold\"}, {\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"characterMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"1774073001914\", \"title\": \"Character\", \"note\": \"wolf\"}}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E1\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"猎人冲入制止狼\", \"color\": \"#0000FF\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \"wolf\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E1\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"猎人冲入制止狼\", \"color\": \"#0000FF\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \" in its tracks. \"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E2\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"猎人制服狼并救出外婆\", \"color\": \"#8B00FF\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \"He swiftly overpowered the beast and freed Grandmother from the wardrobe. \"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"marks\": [{\"type\": \"underline\"}, {\"type\": \"eventMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3-E3\", \"title\": \"Event\", \"note\": \"小红帽与外婆团聚\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}, {\"type\": \"segmentMark\", \"attrs\": {\"id\": \"S3\", \"title\": \"Segment\", \"note\": \"外婆的小屋\", \"color\": \"#FF0000\"}}], \"text\": \"Little Red Riding Hood threw herself into her grandmother's arms, tears streaming down her face. Outside the window, the last ray of sunset broke through the clouds and lit up the little cottage once more.\"}]}]}}","accordion_items":"{\"accordionItems\": [{\"title\": \"Segments\", \"num\": \"3\", \"content\": [{\"id\": \"S1\", \"text\": \"In the early morning,  Little Red Riding Hood 's  garden  was bathed in soft golden light. Her  mother  handed her a basket of pastries and said, \\\" Grandmother  is ill. Take these to her, and do not stray from the  path .\\\"  Little Red Riding Hood nodded, fastened her bright red cloak, and set off toward Grandmother's house.\"}, {\"id\": \"S2\", \"text\": \"Sunlight filtered through the dense canopy, casting dappled shadows along the winding  forest path .  Little Red Riding Hood  walked along with her basket, humming a cheerful tune.  Wildflowers swayed in the breeze, and butterflies danced among the blossoms. She slowed her pace, savoring the peaceful scene. Beside a towering  oak tree , a  wolf  suddenly stepped into her  path .  \\\"Where are you headed, little girl?\\\" he asked with a friendly smile. \\\"I'm going to visit my sick grandmother and bring her some pastries,\\\" she replied innocently.  The wolf tilted his head and pointed toward a flower-lined fork in the road. \\\"That path is shorter, and you could pick some flowers for your grandmother.\\\"  Little Red Riding Hood hesitated, then decided it was a good idea and turned onto the side trail.  The wolf watched her leave, then dashed off in the other direction.\"}, {\"id\": \"S3\", \"text\": \"The wolf reached Grandmother's cottage first, hid the real Grandmother inside the wardrobe, and disguised himself in bed. Dusk was falling as Little Red Riding Hood finally reached the cottage and stepped into the shadowy room. She whispered, \\\"Grandmother, why are your eyes so big?\\\" and then, \\\"And why is your mouth so big?\\\" The wolf threw off the blankets and lunged. Little Red Riding Hood screamed and fell to the floor. At that very moment, the cottage door burst open and a passing Huntsman rushed in with his rifle. He overpowered the beast, freed Grandmother from the wardrobe, and Little Red Riding Hood finally threw herself into her grandmother's arms as sunset light filled the room once more.\"}]}, {\"title\": \"Characters\", \"num\": \"5\", \"content\": [\"Little Red Riding Hood\", \"mother\", \"Grandmother\", \"wolf\", \"huntsman\"]}, {\"title\": \"Locations\", \"num\": \"4\", \"content\": [\"garden\", \"path\", \"forest path\", \"oak tree\"]}, {\"title\": \"KeyEvents\", \"num\": \"12\", \"content\": [{\"id\": \"S1-E1\", \"text\": \"In the early morning,  Little Red Riding Hood 's  garden  was bathed in soft golden light. Her  mother  handed her a basket of pastries and said, \\\" Grandmother  is ill. Take these to her, and do not stray from the  path .\\\" \"}, {\"id\": \"S1-E2\", \"text\": \"Little Red Riding Hood nodded, fastened her bright red cloak, and set off toward Grandmother's house.\"}, {\"id\": \"S2-E1\", \"text\": \"Sunlight filtered through the dense canopy, casting dappled shadows along the winding  forest path .  Little Red Riding Hood  walked along with her basket, humming a cheerful tune. Beside a towering  oak tree , a  wolf  suddenly stepped into her  path . \"}, {\"id\": \"S2-E2\", \"text\": \" Wildflowers swayed in the breeze, and butterflies danced among the blossoms. She slowed her pace, savoring the peaceful scene. \\\"Where are you headed, little girl?\\\" he asked with a friendly smile. \\\"I'm going to visit my sick grandmother and bring her some pastries,\\\" she replied innocently. \"}, {\"id\": \"S2-E3\", \"text\": \"The wolf tilted his head and pointed toward a flower-lined fork in the road. \\\"That path is shorter, and you could pick some flowers for your grandmother.\\\" \"}, {\"id\": \"S2-E4\", \"text\": \"Little Red Riding Hood hesitated, then decided it was a good idea and turned onto the side trail. \"}, {\"id\": \"S2-E5\", \"text\": \"The wolf watched her leave, then dashed off in the other direction.\"}, {\"id\": \"S3-E4\", \"text\": \"The wolf had reached Grandmother's cottage first and hidden the real Grandmother inside the wardrobe. By the time Little Red Riding Hood pushed open the creaking door, the beast was already waiting in bed beneath her grandmother's blankets. She stepped closer and began to question the strange figure in the shadows.\"}, {\"id\": \"S3-E5\", \"text\": \"As Little Red Riding Hood drew nearer, the wolf threw off the blankets and lunged at her. She screamed, stumbled backward, and crashed onto the wooden floor, her basket spilling across the room.\"}, {\"id\": \"S3-E1\", \"text\": \"At that very moment, the cottage door burst open. A passing Huntsman charged in with his rifle and a thunderous shout, startling the wolf and giving Little Red Riding Hood a moment to escape.\"}, {\"id\": \"S3-E2\", \"text\": \"The Huntsman quickly overpowered the wolf, then noticed movement at the wardrobe. He pulled the heavy door open and discovered the real Grandmother hidden inside, frightened but alive.\"}, {\"id\": \"S3-E3\", \"text\": \"Safe at last, Little Red Riding Hood rushed into Grandmother's arms. As the wolf lay defeated on the floor, warm sunset light broke through the cottage window and filled the room with relief.\"}]}]}","beat_first_frame_history":"{\"history\":{\"S1-E1-B1\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B1_46a5ba.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B1_ab15a9.png\"],\"S1-E1-B2\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B2_467672.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B2_40a012.png\"],\"S2-E2-B3\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B3_1.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B3_864ccb.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B3_be7505.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B3_17f725.png\"],\"S2-E2-B4\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B4_c4237e.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B4_b842ec.png\"],\"S2-E2-B1\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B1_b1a70c.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B1_43d0e8.png\"],\"S2-E2-B5\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B5_0d5025.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B5_5fdf91.png\",\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B5_954ae5.png\"],\"S2-E2-B2\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S2-E2-B2_54a0b6.png\"],\"S1-E1-B3\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B3_821163.png\"],\"S1-E1-B4\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B4_b8eb8e.png\"],\"S1-E1-B5\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B5_c95a56.png\"],\"S1-E1-B6\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B6_f95875.png\"],\"S1-E1-B7\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B7_9bc4c7.png\"],\"S1-E1-B8\":[\"http://hdvis.tianeo.com/CompImage/S1-E1-B8_d91a37.png\"]